\id REV - Mupun
\h Suun
\toc3 Sug
\toc2 Suun
\toc1 Mɓe ɗe Jesu Kristi woo nJoon ndǝǝn Suun
\mt2 Mɓe ɗe Jesu Kristi woo
\mt1 nJoon ndǝǝn Suun
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Suun mǝ Jesu kristi ɗǝ Naan Cin wur Kǝ wur woo ɗǝ kǝrem fǝr mo mbii ɗǝ mo kus kǝ ji. Jesu Kristi wur lep ngulep wur dǝm pee kǝrem wur Joon ɗǝ, mbǝkǝ wur woo mbǝ ɗesǝ mo ɗe nwur.
\v 2 Joon wur kǝ ten sat agaak mbii ɗe wur kǝ naa mo jir, kǝ wur ten ran pwoo kǝ Naan ɗe Jesu Kristi woo mo nwur nnee, nǝ a zeen.
\v 3 Koo a weye, ɗe wur tang bǝǝthaal ɗesǝ nǝ, ɓe wur nkat ɗǝret, kǝ nen ɗe mo lekom mbǝ kǝlǝng pwoo ɗesǝ nǝ ɗe Naan kǝ woo nǝ, kǝ moo cin mbǝɗe nǝ sat, ɓe mo nkat ɗeret, mbǝɗe pee nǝ kǝ wul kus, mbǝkǝ mbǝ ɗesǝ nǝ mo ngam ɗǝ.
\s1 Tokshik Joon Dǝm Pǝ // Ekǝlisya Ɗǝ Pwoovǝl Sǝ
\p 
\v 4 Wen Joon kǝn tok kǝ Ekǝlisya ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo, ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil Eshiya.
\q1 Naan wur naa wun shi yit naajeel wur,
\q2 kǝ wur cin tongryang nwun zak.
\q1 Naan ɗe wur ɗe yaksǝ,
\q1 ɗe pǝgyet wur ɗe yam,
\q2 kǝ ɗe wur nɗang jì,
\q1 kǝ Riin ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo,
\q2 ɗe mo ɗar ntom
\q1 kǝ Naan a peetong
\q2 wur ɗǝɗes.
\q1 
\v 5 Kǝ Jesu Kristi,
\q2 ɗe wur a langteng ɗe a zeen,
\q1 wur a ɗinshee,
\q2 ɗe mo shee yool kǝ wur a peemúut,
\q1 kǝ zak, a wur a Mishkoom nkaa
\q2 mishkoom ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil ɗesǝ jir.
\q1 Wur wal mmun a mbǝ muut
\q2 ɗe wur ɓeer toom fin,
\q1 ɓe wur fween mun
\q2 mɓut shikbish fun mo.
\q1 
\v 6 Wur le mǝ ɗee a mishkoom mǝ pris mo,
\q1 mbǝkǝ mǝ seyil ɗe nNaan puun wur.
\q2 Ram, kǝ iiko, mo
\q1 ɗee a mǝ Jesu Kristi
\q2 mbǝ ngaa-ngaa. Nǝ aasǝ!
\q1 
\v 7 Wu naa, wur pǝ jì
\q2 nkaa nluu.
\q1 Gurum mo nnaa wur jir,
\q1 mbe kǝ nen ɗe gyet mo shulang wur.
\q2 Gurum ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil ɗesǝ jir,
\q1 mo nwal maap mbǝ wur.
\q2 Nǝ ndǝǝn aasǝ! Nǝ aasǝ.
\p 
\v 8 Daa Naan ɗeɗes wur sat nǝnee <<a wen ɗe shee kǝ mbǝ mo, kǝ kyes kǝ mbǝ mo jir zak. Naan ɗe wur ɗe yaksǝ, wur ɗe yam, kǝ a wur pǝ jì zak.>>
\s1 Jesu Kristi kámshin nJoon
\p 
\v 9 A an, Joon ɗyemnǝǝn fuu ngudǝm nɗang Jesu, an a memee ndǝǝn wun nen ɗe wuu gung kǝ shwaajeel, mbǝɗe wun a dǝr Mishkoom Kristi. An mee laayil, ɗe am neer nǝ cǝǝrkaat, ɗe moo pet nǝ a Patmos, mbǝɗe gyet an kǝn satpwoo Naan nǝ gurum mo, ɗe Jesu wur shin langteng ne.
\v 10 Parpuus kǝ Daa, ɓe Riin Naan wur jì ɗel ndǝǝn an. Ɗangɓe wen kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ɗeɗes, kaa wal kǝ feer sǝ. Pǝ leshap mbwoon fen.
\v 11 Ɗoo ne sat an nǝnee, << A ran mbǝɗe waa nkaa naa nǝ, kǝ a lep kǝ ɓǝǝthaal nǝ dǝ Ekǝlisya ɗepwoovǝl sǝ mo, ɗe mo nyilkaam, Afisus kǝ Simena, kǝ Pagamum, kǝ Tayatǝra, kǝ Sardis, kǝ Filadalfiya, kǝ Lodisiya.>>
\p 
\v 12 Wen cǝǝr mbǝkǝ an naa ngwe ɗe wur katpwoo nǝ ɗǝ. Kaaɗe an cǝǝr, ɓe an naa, peele ngyem mo pwoovǝl, ɗe mo ɗak mo a shi zinariya.
\v 13 Nnaar kǝ peele ngyem ɗe pwoovǝl ɗesǝ nǝ mo, ɓe an naa mee gwar wur ɗar ɗǝ, ɗe wur lapshak kǝ Làa Gurum. Wur lep mee nlǝr ɗe nǝ sham wul wur nkwakshii, kǝ wur ɓwoot mee teng sǝ cǝǝr nkaa tuur wur, ɗe mo ɗak mǝnǝ a shi zinariya.
\v 14 Shwepkáa wur nǝ mo piyaa kaa shuu sǝ, kǝ nǝ kaa ɗoor sǝ. Yit wur nǝ mo lapwus kaa liis kǝ wus sǝ.
\v 15 Shi wur mo mǝlep, kaa shool ɗemǝlep, ɗe mo tap ɗak shi wus mbǝkǝ nǝ ɗee a ɗeret sǝ. Ɗoo wur nǝ a kaa wal kǝ am ɗe moo sham mpǝtuul sǝ.
\v 16 Wur kǝ zar mo pwoovǝl nsarse wur, kǝ mee kwai ɗi se put pwoo wur ɗe nǝ se koop weet. Yit wur nǝ fes ɓangpee hakyeng kaa puus a naar sǝ.
\p 
\v 17 Kaaɗe an naa wur, ɓe an taa nyil nder shii wur kaa an kǝn mumuut sǝ. Ɓe wur le sarse wur nkaa an, ɗangɓe wur sat nǝnee, <<Taji kǝǝrmuut yaa waa kas. A an a ɗinshee, kǝ a an a kyes ne.
\v 18 A an a ɗe mmeen. Gyet an kǝn muut, mɓe yaksǝ, ɓe an kǝ seen. Wen ntong ɗe kǝ seen mbe ngaa-ngaa. Wen kǝ mbii wang peemúut, kǝ peedǝm kǝ nen mumuut mo, a sar fǝn.
\p 
\v 19 <<A ran mbǝɗe aa ten a naa mo yaksǝ, kǝ mbǝɗe waa nkaa naa mo, kǝ mbǝɗe mo mbǝ jì.
\v 20 A ɗesǝ nǝ a shii kǝ zar ɗesǝsok ɗe pwoovǝl ɗe mo nsarse fen, kǝ peeɗar mǝ ngyem ɗe pwoovǝl ɗe mo ɗak a shi zinariya. Zar ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo, a mo a nenlep kǝ Ekǝlisya ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo, kǝ peeɗar kǝ ngyem ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo, mo a Ekǝlisya ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo zak.>>
\c 2
\s1 Lep dǝm pee Ekǝlisya // ɗe nǝn nyil Afisus
\p 
\v 1 <<A ran shi dǝm lep-Naan ɗe Ekǝlisya ɗi Sarduis wur ɗen Ekǝlisya ɗe nǝn nyil Afisus nǝnee, << Lep ɗesǝ nǝ, a pwoo ɗe nǝ put mpwoo kǝ gwar ɗe wur kǝ zar mo pwoovǝl nsarse wur sǝ, ɗe wur mwaan nnaar kǝ peele ngyem ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo, ɗe mo ɗak mo a shi zinariya sǝ.
\v 2 Wen man ɗak ɗe wun kǝ ten cin nǝ, kǝ jeel fuu, kǝ gung fuu zak. Baa wuu shaar kǝ nenɗebish mo kas. Wuu cam shiimwaan kǝ nen ɗe mo sat nǝnee, << wuɗun a jeplep Jesu mo, mɓe baa mo a jeplep Kristi kas. Wuu ten wu man ne, moo cin a ɗung.
\v 3 Wu gung, koo ɗe wun nkaa shwaajeel mbǝ sǝm fen, ɓe taji wu baa mɓwoon kas.
\v 4 Amma an ɗe kǝ mee mbii mǝndong nkaa wun ɗe an kǝn rǝɓet sat nǝ nwun. Baa wu kuɗi wuu wal nghan kaa ɗe gyet wuu wal an nshee sǝ kas.
\v 5 Taji wu mander nshiimwaan fuu ɗe gyet yam, akuɗang wuu táa wu pal sǝ kas. Wu tuwap, mbǝkǝ wu baa wu mwaan ɗe ndǝǝn ar nǝ, kaa gyet yam sǝ. Katɗang baa wu tuwap kas, ɓe an mbǝ jì, kǝ an mang peele ngyem nǝ ɗe a peeɗar ni.
\v 6 Ɗangbe mbǝ mbii mǝndong ɗe an kǝ kwoop wun mbǝ nǝ a nɗǝsi, baa ɗyeen wun mbǝ ɗak nen Nikolaitan mo kas, kaaɗǝ baa nǝ a ɗyeen fen kas sǝ.
\p 
\v 7 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom, mbǝ kǝlǝngpee ɓe wur kǝlǝng mbǝɗe Riin nǝ nkaa sat nǝ nendǝm ɗangnaan mo, <<Ngwe ɗe wur se koorong, ɓe an ncin pee nwur se laatǝng ɗe nǝ a mǝ seen, ɗe nǝ kàa ndǝǝn bong kǝ Naan.>>
\s1 Lep Dǝm Pee Ekǝlisya // Ɗe Nǝn nYil nSimena
\p 
\v 8 <<A ran lep dǝm pee ngulep Naan ɗe wur ɗǝǝn Ekǝlisya ɗe nǝn nyil nSimena nǝnee, <<Lep ɗesǝ nǝ a pwoo ɗe nǝ put mpwoo kǝ gwar ɗe wur a ɗinshee, kǝ a wur a kyes kǝ mbǝ mo jir, ɗe gyet wur kǝ muut, mɓe yaksǝ wur kǝ seen.
\p 
\v 9 Wen man shwa jeel fuu mo kǝ jeel fuu, kǝ zak, nghan man nǝnee, << Jir kǝ sǝ wun a nenlong mo. Wen man pwoo ɗebish mǝ nen ɗe moo lesut a nen Yahudi mo, ɓe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas. Mo a nen kǝ ngujwaan mo.
\v 10 Taji wu kat mee kǝǝrmuut nkaa jeel ɗe wun mbǝ shwaa nǝ kas. A kǝleng, nGujwaan wur cam wun. Wur nle pak fuu mo ndǝǝn lushoot, wun nshwaajeel mbǝ teer mo kaapaat. Mbe wu gung, taji wu cii an kas, koo ɗe mo ntǝtwe wun, ɓe wu gung, mbǝkǝ an cin biikaa koorong mǝ seen ɗeɗes nwun.
\p 
\v 11 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom, ɓe wur kǝlǝng mbǝɗe Riin wur nkaa sat nǝ (Ekǝlisya) nendǝm ndang Naan mo. Ngwe ɗe wur se koorong, ɓe baa muut ɗe vǝl nǝn ntung wur kas.>>
\s1 Lep Dǝm Pee Ekǝlisya // Ɗe Nǝn nYil Pagamum
\p 
\v 12 <<A ran lep dǝm pee ngulep Naan ɗe wur Ekǝlisya ɗe nen nyil Pagamum nǝ, Lep ɗesǝ nǝ put a mpwoo kǝ gwar ɗe wur kǝ kwai ɗe nǝ se koop vǝl sǝ.
\v 13 Wen man, npee ɗe wuu tong ɗe nǝ, ɓe ngujwaan wur kǝ le mpeetong fǝn a pee mǝ nǝ. jir kǝsǝ ɓe wuu yaa sǝm fǝn ɓalɓal. Baa wu nyan shin zeenpwoo fǝn kas, kaaɗǝ gyet ɗǝǝn teer mǝ Antipas mo ngucìn langteng fǝn mɓǝ mo tu wur nɗǝǝn yilkaam fu peeɗe shetaan kǝ tong.
\p 
\v 14 Mbe an kǝ rep pak mbǝ mo lee nkaa wun. Wun kǝ pak gurum mo nnaar fuu, ɗe moo dǝm a nɗang kám mǝ Balaam. Gyet a Balaam wur kám mBalak, kǝ wur gangkwak nen Izrel mo, mbe gyet mo shin shikbish mbǝ se mbiise ɗe gyet mo kǝ ten cin nkùm, kǝ cin mbǝ ɗebish mo kaa ngaa sǝ.
\v 15 Kǝzak, wun kǝ nen ɗe moo dǝm nɗang kám nǝn Nikolaus mo.
\v 16 Wu tuwap, kas ɓe an kus kǝ jì, kun cin lek ɗe kǝ wun, shi kwai fǝn ɗe nǝ jì put mpwoo fǝn sǝ.
\p 
\v 17 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom, mbǝ kǝlǝngpee, ɓe wur kǝlǝng mbǝɗe Riin Naan wur nkaa sat nǝ Ekǝlisya nendǝm ndang Naan mo.>>
\p Ngwe ɗe wur se koorong, ɓe nghan ncin pak man ɗe nǝ a sǝsok nwur. Kǝ zak, an ncin jwak ɗepiyaa ngwar nǝ, kǝ sǝm ɗepwoo a rǝran ɗi kǝ nkaa jwak nǝ. Gwar ɗe wur nlap jwak nǝ, ɓe a wur man mbǝɗe mo ran nkaa nǝ ɓejee ɗak.
\s1 Lep Dǝm Pee Ekǝlisya // Ɗe nYil nTayatira
\p 
\v 18 <<A ran lep dǝm pee ngulep Naan ɗe wur tap kǝ Ekǝlisya ɗe nǝn nyil nTayatǝra nǝ, Lep ɗesǝ nǝ put a mpwoo kǝ Làa kǝ Naan ɗe yit wur moo lapwus kaa mbǝlem kǝ wus sǝ, ɗe shii wur moo mǝlep kaa shool ɗe mo tap ɗak nǝ sǝ.
\v 19 Wen man ɗak fuu mo, kǝ wal fuu, kǝ cinzeen fuu, kǝ ɗak ɓam ɗe wu cin mo, kǝ gung fuu, kǝ zak, yaksǝ ɓe wun nkaa cin ɗak nǝ met ɗe gyet wu cin mo nshee.
\v 20 Mbǝ jir kǝsǝ, ɓe an kǝ mbǝ ɗesǝ mo nkaa ɗel ɗekǝ ɗǝsǝ moo nkaa wun. Mɓeɗe wu tap wu kiyee mat ɗe moo pet war a Jezebel sǝ, ɗe war pet set a mat satpwoo kǝ Naan. A shi ar kám war, ɓe war le kǝ kǝrem fǝn mo cin mbǝ ɗebish mo kaa cin ngaa, kǝ se mbiise ɗe mo kǝ ten cin nkùm.
\v 21 Wen kǝn shin pee nwar, mbǝkǝ war tuwap ɗǝ, ɓe war cii tuwap mbǝ shikbish war, ɗe nǝ a mǝ ngaa.
\v 22 Wen nle kǝ shwal yaa war ɗǝ, kǝ nen ɗe moo cin ngaa ashak kǝ war, katɗang baa mo tuwap kas, kǝ mo nook cin mbii ɗebish mǝnǝ mo kas, ɓe nghan shin jeel mo.
\v 23 Wen nle kǝ jep war mo murep kǝ shwal, mbǝkǝ Ekǝlisya mo jir mo man ɗi nǝnee, << an a ngwe ɗe an kǝn man pan ɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn pǝtuup gurum mo, kǝ zak, an kǝn leng pǝtuup mo mo. Wen nkwat koo a weye nciit kǝ ɗak ɗe ngwe nǝ kǝ ten cin.
\p 
\v 24 Yaksǝ kǝn nsat wun koor nen Tayatǝra, ɗe baa wu lap kám nǝ kas, baa wu man mbii ɗebish, ɗe gurum moo pet nǝ a ɗe sǝsok ndǝr mǝ Shetan kas, baa an le teng kaa wun kǝ mee leeton kas.
\v 25 Wu ɗar ɓalɓal nɗǝǝn mbiiɗe wuu ten wu kám, ɗang mbaa njì.
\p 
\v 26 mbe gwar ɗe wur se koorong, ɗang wur cin ɗyen fǝn, dǝm sul, an shin ɓal nkaa yil nǝ mo.
\v 27 Mo ncìn mulki nkaa yil nǝ mo, a shi kám shool, ɗang mo mpyan mo, a kaa tuulwan ɗe gurum kǝ piin nǝ sǝ, kaaɗe wen kǝn kat ɓal nsar puun fen sǝ
\v 28 ɓe an nshin zar mangɓit ngwar mǝnǝ.
\v 29 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom, mbǝ kǝlǝngpee, ɓe wur kǝlǝng mbǝɗe Riin Naan nǝ sat luu Naan nǝ mo>>
\c 3
\s1 Lep dǝm pee Ekǝlisya // ɗe nǝ nyil nSardis
\p 
\v 1 <<A ran lep dǝm shi dǝm ngulep Naan ɗe Ekǝlisya ɗe nǝ nyil nSardis nǝnee, << A lep nǝ nɗesǝ, ɗe nǝ put a mpwoo kǝ gwar ɗe wur kǝ Riin Naan mo pwoovǝl, kǝ zar mo pwoovǝl zak.
\p Wen man ɗak fwa, waa le kǝ gurum mo pan nnee, waa ɗe kǝ seen, mɓe waa a ɗemumuut.
\v 2 A yool atǝng, mbǝkǝ a fwang rep koor seen ɗe nǝ ɗee nǝ ɗe, mbǝkǝ taji nǝ sǝǝt muut kǝnding-nding. Wen naa, baa shiimwaan fwa nǝ a ɗeret nyit kǝ Naan kas.
\v 3 Mɓemǝnǝ, ɓe nghan kǝn sat nwaa, a pan mbǝɗe gyet aa ten a kǝlǝng mo, ɗe gyet mbe aa lap mo. A cinzeen mǝnǝ mo ɓalɓal. A yool, Katɗang baa waa yool kas, ɓe an mbaajì a kaa wat sǝ, ɗe baa waa mman parpuus baaji fǝn nǝ kas.
\p 
\v 4 Mbe rep pak gurum mo ɗe, nyil nSardis, ɗe mo tap le lée mo mo a ɗeɓang. Nen mǝnǝ moo mwaan ashak kǝ nghan. Mo nlep lée ɗepiyaa-piyaa mo, mbǝɗe shiimwaan fur nǝ mo ret.
\v 5 Nen ɗe mo se koorong, ɓe mo nlep lée ɗepiyaa-piyaa mo zak. Baa an ncam tu sǝm mo nɗǝǝn bǝǝthaal mǝ nenseen mo kas. Kǝ lep wur mo, ɓe an nsat agaak ne, mo a nen fen mo akyeen Naan, kǝ kǝkyeen Jeplep wur mo.
\v 6 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom mbǝ kǝlǝngpee, ɓe wur kǝlǝng mbii ɗe Riin Naan wur nkaa sat nǝ nen lu Naan mo.>>
\s1 Lep dǝm pee Ekǝlisya // ɗe nǝn nyil nFiladalfiya
\p 
\v 7 <<A ran lep dǝm pee ngulep Naan ɗe wur kǝ tap Ekǝlisya ɗe nǝn nyil nFiladalfiya.
\p <<Lep ɗesǝ nǝ put a mpwoo kǝ gwar ɗe wur a ɗeɓang kǝ wur azeen. A wur kǝ makuli kǝ Devid. Katɗang wur wang pwoolu nǝ, ɓe baa mee gurum mak shoot nǝ kas, kǝ zak, katɗang wur shoot pee nǝ, ɓe baa mee gurum mmak wang nǝ kas.
\p 
\v 8 Wen man ɗak fwa. A naa, an kǝn ten wangpee nwaa, ɗe baa mee ngwe mmak shoot nǝ kas. Wen man nǝnee, << koo ɗe baa ɓal fwa nǝ ɗes kas, ɓe waa aa ɗar ɓalɓal nɗǝǝn pwoo fen, kǝ zak, baa waa ciipwoo nǝnee a nook man an kas.
\v 9 A kǝleng, an nle nen mǝ ngujwaan ɗe moo le sut a nen Yahudi sǝ mo, mɓe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas, moo cin a ɗung. Wen nle kǝ nenɗung ɗesǝ mo jì kurum ntoom fwa, kǝ nder shii fwa, kǝ mo man ɗe zak nǝnee, << an wal nwaa.
\v 10 Kaaɗe aa ten a keer war fen sǝ mo, kǝ gung zak, mpeemǝnǝ ɓe nghan ntap kǝ waa, mbǝkǝ taji mee mbii tung waa kas, nɗǝǝn teer mǝ jeel ɗe nǝn nɗang jì nkaa yil nǝ, mbǝkǝ nǝ cam gurum mo ɗe jir nɗǝǝn ɓǝm-yil ne.
\p 
\v 11 Wen nɗang jì kǝlak-kǝlak. A yaa mbǝɗe waa kǝ nǝ ɓalɓal, mbǝkǝ taji, mee gurum mang zuum mǝ koorong nǝ kas.
\v 12 Jir gwar ɗe wur se koorong, ɓe an nle kǝ war ɗen a kaa ndwet mǝ Lu Naan ɗeɗes Naan fen. Ɗe baa nǝ ncam put ɗe nɗǝǝn Lu Naan nǝ kas. Wen nran sǝm Naan fǝn nkaa mo, kǝ sǝm mǝ yil Naan fen, Jerusalem ɗepwoo, ɗe nǝ tong a ɗeng sham pǝ Naan fen ɗǝ, kǝzak, an nran sǝm fǝn ɗepwoo nkaa mo.
\v 13 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom mbǝ kǝlǝngpee, ɓe wur kǝlǝng mbǝɗe Riin Naan wur nkaa sat nen dǝm ndang Naan mo.>>
\s1 Lep dǝm pee Ekǝlisya // ɗe nǝn nyil nLodisiya
\p 
\v 14 Gwar nǝ sat nghan nǝnee, <<A ran lep dǝm pee ngulep kǝ Naan ɗe wur tap kǝ Ekǝlisya ɗe nǝn nyil nLodisiya.
\p <<Lep ɗesǝ nǝ put a mpwoo kǝ gwar ɗe moo pet wur a Amin. Shi kǝ mǝnǝ nǝnee, <nǝ aasǝ> Wur a ngwe ɗe azeen-nzeen, kǝ wur a langteng ɗe azeen. A wur a kuk kǝ mbǝɗe Naan wur le mo jir.
\v 15 Wen man ɗak fwa, baa waa a ɗezuum koo ɗetal kas. Ngyel ɗe waa a ɗezuum, koo ɗetal.
\v 16 mbǝɗe waa anaar-anaar, baa waa a ɗetal kas, koo ɗezuum kas, mpeemǝnǝ, ɓe an mbe wut waa put aku mɓut mpwoo fǝn.
\v 17 Waa sat nǝnee, << waa kǝ long, kǝ waa kat mbii mo jir! Mɓǝ baa aa reɓet mee mbii kas. Ɗangɓe baa waa man nǝ nghaa kǝ mbii kas, nghaa bii yitmwaa, ngu jeel, vuum, kǝ ngum.
\p 
\v 18 Wen pǝ shin kar wun kǝ wu seet zinariya ɗǝret ɗǝ mo ɗak shi wus pǝ nghan mbǝkǝ a ɗee ɗe a ngulong. A seet lée ɗepiyaa mo pǝ nghan ɗi, mbǝkǝ a paa gum bii naashweep fwa ɗi. A jì a seet yen mǝ yit zak, mbǝkǝ a le ɗe nyit fwa mo, mbǝkǝ a naapee ɗi.
\p 
\v 19 Nen ɗe wen kǝn wal mo, a mo a nen ɗe kǝn gwak mo inn le more kaa ar. Mɓemǝnǝ, ɓe wu ɗar azeen-nzeen, mbǝkǝ wu tuwap ɗi.
\v 20 An sǝsǝ kǝn ɗar mpwoolu nǝ pǝ ɓwap pee. Katɗang mee ngwe kǝlǝng ɗoo fen, ɗang gwar nǝ wang pwoolu nǝ, ɓe nghan nɗel nɗǝǝn lu nǝ, mɓǝ nghan se mbiise ashak kǝ gwar mǝnǝ, kǝ gwar mǝne nse mbiise ashak kǝ nghan zak.
\p 
\v 21 Gwe ɗe wu se koorong, ɓe wen shin pee mo, mbǝkǝ mo tong ɗe ashak kǝ nghan nkaa mbetong mǝ mulki fen, kaaɗe gyet wen kǝn se koorong sǝ. Wen kǝn tong ashak kǝ puun fen nkaa mbǝtong mǝ mulki wur.
\v 22 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom mbǝ kǝlǝngpee, ɓe wu kǝlǝng mbǝɗe Riin nǝ nkaa sat nǝ lunaan mo.>>
\c 4
\s1 Seyil nNaan aɗeng
\p 
\v 1 Aɓwoon mǝnǝ, ɓe an ɗiyeep yit fǝn. Ɓe an naa mee polu ɗe nǝ a wuwang nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, ɓe an kǝlǝng ɗoo ɗe nǝ wal nciit kǝ feer, ɗe ɗí nǝ katpwoo kǝ an nshee. Nǝ sat an nǝnee, <<A kàa mpesi. Wen nkám nwaa mbǝɗe ting mo ncìn aɓwoon mbii ɗesǝ mo.>>
\v 2 Aɓet-Aɓet, ɓe Riin Naan wur jì ɗel nɗǝǝn an, ɗangɓe nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, ɓe an naa mee peetong mǝ mulki, ɗe mee gwar kǝ tong nkaa ne.
\v 3 Yit kǝ gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa nǝ, nii lapwus kaa jwak ɗeret ɗe moo pet mo a jaspa, kǝ kaneliyan, kǝ lilliu ɗe nǝ lapshak kǝ mee jwak ɗe moo pet nǝ a emiral, mo tap neer peetong mǝ mulki nǝ cǝǝrkaat.
\v 4 Mee peetong mǝ mulki mo laarvǝl baafeer, mo neer peetong mǝ mulki nǝ le nnaar. Nennan mo laarvǝl baafeer, moo tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki ɗiisi nǝ mo. Nennan ɗesǝ nǝ mo, moo lep a lée ɗepiyaa-piyaa mo, kǝ zak, mo lep a mbekáa mǝ mulki, ɗe mo ɗak mo a shi zinariya.
\v 5 Mǝlep kǝ pee kǝ put ɗe nɗǝǝn peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, kǝ or ɗeɗes kǝ nluu pǝrep. Akiyeen kǝ peetong mǝ mulki ɗesǝ nǝ mo, ɓe ngyem mo pwoovǝl mo nkaa lapwus. A ɗesǝ nǝ mo a Riin Naan ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo.
\v 6 Kǝzak, akyeen kǝ peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, ɓe an naa mee mbǝ káa baahar sǝ, ɗe nǝ mǝlep kaa gǝlas sǝ, kǝ nǝ ɗong kyet-kyet. Mee mbǝɗe mo kǝ seen, mo feer, moo ɗar peefeer, cǝǝr mɓwoon kǝ peetong mǝ mulki ɗeɗes nǝ, mbǝ ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen nǝ mo, mo gam kǝ yit nkoop mɓwoon kǝ nkoop ndǝǝn.
\v 7 Ɗin nshee nǝ, lapshak kǝ nvar, ɗevǝl nǝ lapshak kǝ kus randong, ɗekun nǝ, ɓe yit kǝ nǝ nciit kǝ mǝ gurum, ɗefeer nǝ lapshak kǝ puul ɗe nǝ nkaa yool ncáap sǝ.
\v 8 Koo a ɗeɗangyi ndǝǝn mbǝɗe mo kǝ seen feer ɗesǝ nǝ mo, ɓe nǝ kǝ cáap mo peemee, kǝ mo kǝ yit cǝǝr kat kǝ nɗer caap mo. Mpar kǝ puus, baa mo nok sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Ɗǝɓang, ɗeɓang, ɗeɓang,
\q2 a wur a ɗe yam,
\q1 kǝ a wur a ɗe yaksǝ,
\q2 kǝ a wur a ɗǝ mǝ ji zak.>>
\m 
\v 9 Kaaɗe mbii ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen ɗesǝ mo, mo kwoop, kǝ mo cin ɗeɗes mǝ pǝlang, pee gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, a wur ɗe wur kǝ seen mbe ngaa-ngaa.
\v 10 ɓe Nennan ɗe laarvǝl baafeer sǝ mo, mo zǝm ntoom kǝ gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, mo seyil nwur. Wur ɗe wur mmeen mbe ngaa-ngaa. Nennan ɗesǝ nǝ mo shwat mbiikáa ɗe mǝ mulki mo mo ntoom wur, ɗang mo nkaa sat nǝnee,
\q1 
\v 11 <<Daa Naan fun
\q2 a waa mak lap ram,
\q1 kǝ kwoop, kǝ ɓal
\q2 A waa ɗak mbǝ mo ɗe jir,
\q1 A shi pan fwa ɓe
\q1 waa ɗak mo ɗǝ, kǝzak,
\q2 A waa cin nseen mo.>>
\c 5
\s1 Ɓǝǝt-haal ɗeciciɓet kǝ Laatǝm
\p 
\v 1 Wen naa mee ɓǝǝt haal ɗe nǝ a ciciɓet nɗǝǝn sarse kǝ gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki nǝ. Mo ran-ran nkaa ɓǝǝt haal ɗesǝ nǝ, nkoop mɓwoon kǝ nkoop nɗǝǝn zak. Mo lus mo pwoovǝl shi stam.
\v 2 Ɗangɓe wen naa mee ngulep kǝ Naan ɗǝɗes, ɗe wur nkaa satpwoo ɓalɓal nǝnee, <<A wii mmak fǝlǝp káa kǝ <<stam ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo, <<mbe kǝ wur wang ɓǝǝthaal <<ɗeciciɓet nǝ ɗe ye?>>
\m 
\v 3 Mbe baa mee gurum nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, koo nɗǝǝn yil ɗese, koo nder kǝ yil nǝ, ɗe wur mak wang ɓǝǝt haal ɗesǝ nǝ, kǝ wur mak naa ɗǝǝn nǝ ɗe kas.
\v 4 Ɓe wen wal hakyeng, mbǝɗe baa mo kat mee gurum ɗe wur mak wang ɓǝǝthaal nǝ, koo naa ɗǝǝn nǝ kas.
\v 5 Ɗangɓe memee nɗǝǝn nennan nǝ mo, sat an nǝnee, <<Taji a wal kas, a naa mbwoor nɗang kǝ Juda, kǝ nɗang kǝ Devid wur kǝ se koorong. Wur mmak fǝlǝp nbii ɗe mo lwas nǝ, kǝ wur wang ɓǝǝt haal nǝ, kǝ mbii lwas ɗepwoovǝl nǝ mo.>>
\p 
\v 6 Ɗangɓe an naa mee Laatǝm kǝ naapee kaa ɗe ge gap sǝ, kǝ ɗar nnaar kǝ peetong mǝ mulki nǝ mo, mo neer wur cǝǝr kat kǝ mbǝ ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ mo, kǝ nennan ɗe sǝ mo. Laatǝm ɗesǝ nǝ kǝ soom mo pwoovǝl, kǝ yit mo pwoovǝl zak. Ɗese nǝ mo a Riin kǝ Naan ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo, ɗe Naan wur lep mo koo a pee ɗeɗangyi nɗǝǝn yil ɗese.
\v 7 Laatǝm ɗesǝ nǝ yool dǝm lap ɓǝǝt haal ɗeciciɓet ɗe nǝ nsarse kǝ gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki ne.
\v 8 Kaaɗe wur lap ɓǝǝthaal ɗesǝ nǝ, ɓe mbǝɗe mo kǝ seen feer sǝ mo, kǝ nennan ɗe laarvǝl baafeer sǝ mo, mo kurum nyil, ntoom kǝ Laatǝm nǝ. Koo a weye nɗǝǝn nennan ɗe laarvǝl baafeer sǝ mo, ɓe mo kǝ nɗeng-nɗeng, mo kǝ yaa ɗaa shool, zinariya, ɗe nǝ gam kǝ mee mbiizuum ɗeshang. Mbiizuum ɗesǝ nǝ a ɗangnaan kǝ nen kǝ Naan mo.
\v 9 Mo mang mee kook ɗepwoo nǝnee,
\q1 <<A wa a mak
\q2 mbǝ a mang ɓǝǝt haal nǝ,
\q1 kǝ a wang lwas nǝ mo,
\q2 mbǝɗe gyet mo kǝ tu waa,
\q1 kǝ a shi toom fwa,
\q2 ɓe a waa seet gurum mo ɗes,
\q1 kǝ a jì kǝ mo nDaa Naan.
\q2 Nen ɗe waa seet nǝ mo,
\q1 mo put a ndǝǝn koo a soon ɗeɗangyii.
\q2 Kǝ koo a ndǝǝn lespwoo ɗeɗangyii,
\q1 kǝ koo a nɗǝǝn gurum ɗeɗang mo yii,
\q2 kǝ koo a nɗǝǝn yil ɗeɗangyii zak.
\q1 
\v 10 Waa le mo ɗee a mishkoom,
\q2 kǝ mo ɗee a pris mo cin ɗak nNaan fun,
\q1 kǝzak, mo se mulki nkaa mo nɗǝǝn yil ne.
\p 
\v 11 Kaaɗe naapee, ɓe an kǝlǝng ɗoo kǝ nenlep Naan mo ɗes, ɗe mo ngal kaapaat nkaa ngal kaapaat, ɗe mo neer peetong mǝ mulki nǝ cǝǝrkaat, kǝ mbii ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ mo, mo neer mbetong mǝ mulki nǝ kǝ Nennan sǝ mo.
\v 12 Mo cin kook shi ɗoo ɗeɗes nǝnee,
\q1 <<Laatǝm ɗe gyet mo kǝ tu nǝ,
\q2 a wur mak lap,
\q1 iiko kǝ long, kǝ seen, kǝ ɓal,
\q2 kǝ ɗeɗes kǝ ram, kǝ kwoop.>>
\p 
\v 13 Ɗangɓe an kǝlǝng mbǝɗe mo ɗak mo jir, ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, kǝ ɗe mo nɗǝǝn yil, kǝ ɗe mo nder kǝ yil, kǝ ɗe mo nkaa am, kǝ mbǝɗe mo nɗǝǝn mo jir, mo cin kook nǝnee,
\q1 <<Mbee wur ɗe wuu tong nkaa
\q1 peetong mǝ mulki,
\q2 kǝ Laatǝm, wu yit kǝ mǝ kwoop wur,
\q1 kǝ shin ɗeɗes nwur,
\q1 kǝ ram, kǝ iiko
\q2 kǝ ɓal ngaa-ngaa.>>
\p 
\v 14 Ɗangɓe mbǝɗe mo kǝ seen feer sǝ mo sat nǝnee, <<nǝ akǝ sǝ.> ɗang Nennan sǝ mo nkurum furum, kǝ mo seyil ɗe nwur.
\c 6
\s1 Mbiiluwaspee mo
\p 
\v 1 Wen naa kaaɗe Laatǝm nǝ, fulep mbii luwaspee ɗinshee mɓwut ɗepwoovǝl sǝ mo. Ɗangɓe an kǝlǝng ɗoo kǝ memee mɓut mbǝ ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ. Wur petpee shi ɗoo ɗeɓal kaa kwòot kǝ nluu sǝ nǝnee, << Jì!>>
\v 2 Kaaɗe wen naapee, ɓe wen naa mee bǝrǝng ɗepiyaa kǝ ji akyeen fen. Gwar ɗe wur lang bǝrǝng ɗesǝ, wur kǝ nree nsar wur. Mo shin mbiikáa ɗǝɗes nwur, wur jì put kaa ɓǝrǝng nǝ kaa gu koorong sǝ, mɓe kǝ wur sǝ koorong ɗi.
\p 
\v 3 Kaaɗe Laatǝm nǝ fulep mbii lwaspee ɗevǝl nǝ, ɓe wen kǝlǝng mbii ɗevǝl ɗǝ kǝ seen sǝ mo, sat nǝnee, << jì!>>
\v 4 Ɗangɓe mee bǝring npoo jì put, nǝ a naat. Gwar ɗe wur lang bǝring ɗenaat ɗesǝ nǝ, mo shin iiko nwur mbǝkǝ wur mang tongryang baa kǝ nǝ aku ndǝǝn yil ɗese, mbǝkǝ gurum mo ɗoom twe shak ɗi. mo shin mee kwai ɗeɗes nwur zak.
\p 
\v 5 Kaaɗe Laatǝm nǝ fulep mbii luwaspee ɗekun nǝ, ɓe wen kǝlǝng mbii ɗekun, ɗe kǝ seen nǝ sat nǝnee, <<Jì!>> naapee, ɓe naa bǝring ɗetǝp a kyeen fen. Gwar ɗe wur lang bǝring ɗetǝp nǝ, wur kǝ mbii kám mbii mo nɗǝǝn sar fǝn.
\v 6 ɓe nkǝlǝng mee mbii kaa ɗoo sǝ, ndǝǝn mbǝ ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ, ɗoo nǝ sat nǝnee, <<Gurum mmang shool ɗak wur, mǝ puus mǝndong, kǝ wur seet muuduu mǝ alkama ɗe mǝndong, kǝ zak, gurum mang shool ɗak wur, mǝ puus mǝndong, kǝ wur seet muuduu mo kun mǝ shwanan ɗǝ. Mbe taji a tǝkook kǝ mwoor nǝ kǝ am anab nǝ kas.>>
\p 
\v 7 Kaaɗe Laatǝm nǝ fulep mbii luwaspee ɗefeer nǝ, ɓe wen kǝlǝng ɗoo kǝ ɗefeer mɓut mbǝɗe mo kǝ seen nǝ wur sat nǝnee, <<Jì!>>
\v 8 Ool mee bǝring sǝ, nǝ a vuun, akyeen fǝn, moo pet gwar ɗe wur lang bǝring ɗesǝ a muut, kǝ peetong nǝ nenmuut mo mɓwoon nwur. Mo cin iiko mo nkaa mǝndong mɓut feer kǝ yil nǝ, mbǝkǝ mo twe gurum mo shi kwai, kǝ neen, kǝ muut, kǝ luwayil mo zak.
\p 
\v 9 Kaaɗe wur fulep mbiiluwaspee ɗepaat nǝ, ɓe wen naa nder kǝ peewus mbezuum. A seen kǝ nen ɗe gyet mo twe mo, mbǝɗe gyet mo satpwoo Naan nǝ, kǝ zak, mo ɗar kaa shin zeen fur.
\v 10 Mo petpee shi ɗoo ɗeɗes <<Daa Naan ɗǝɗes, ɗeɓang, kǝ ɗe waa azeen, <<a pǝrang ɗang wen ntokɗyeel nenyil nǝ mo ye? <<Nen ɗe gyet mo twe mun sǝ mo, <<mɓǝkǝ waa laa kwat mo ɗe yii?>>
\m 
\v 11 Koo aweyi ɗǝǝn mo mo shin lée ɗepiyaa mo jwal. Ɗang mo waa sat mo nǝnee, <<Wu gung ɗelee aku, kǝ ɗuu kǝ shaar ɗak fuu mo, kǝ ɗyemnǝǝn fuu ɗe mo ntwe mo, kaaɗe mo twe wun sǝ,
\p 
\v 12 Naa Laatǝm nǝ fulep mbii luwaspee ɗepeemee nǝ, ɓe naa yil nǝ yoon ɗes zam, ɗangɓe puus nǝ cǝǝr ɗee a tǝp kaa nlǝr maap, ɗe moo ɗak shi shweep ghǝ sǝ, kǝ tar nǝ cǝǝr ɗee a naat kaa toom sǝ.
\v 13 Zar mo ndǝǝn ɗengnaan, mbe mo sham ɗyong nyil, kaaɗǝ laatǝng kyeen ɗenung moo ɗyong nyil, katɗang kut cutpee ɓalɓal sǝ.
\v 14 Ɗengnaan nǝ ɗel loom kaa garvit ɗe mo cǝɓet sǝ, mo shang jir zuul nǝ mo, kǝ yil ɗe am neer mo le nnaar, baa kǝ nǝ pee mo ɗe.
\p 
\v 15 Ɗangɓe mishkoom mǝ yil nǝ mo, kǝ nen ɗe mo se mulki mo, Ke jep mishkoom mo kǝ ɗenan-nan mǝ shiitoon mo, kǝ nenlong mo, kǝ nen ɗe mo kǝ iiko mo, kǝ koor gurum mo jir, kǝrem mo, kǝ jeplu mo, mo dǝm loom ndǝǝn gwoot mo, kǝ goop zuul mo.
\v 16 Mo pǝt Zuul nǝ mo kǝ jwak nǝ mo nǝnee, <<Wu jì wu taa nkaa mun, kǝ wun paa mun yit gwar ɗe wur kǝ tong nkaa mulki nǝ kǝ tuup Laatǝm nǝ.
\v 17 Mɓeeɗe puus tuup mo ɗeɗes nii jì wul. A wii mmak ɗar pwoo nǝ mpuus mǝnǝ yii?>>
\c 7
\s1 Gurum mo Ngal Kambil Mǝndong kǝ Lar Feer // Ba Feer Ɗeluluwas
\p 
\v 1 Aɓwoon ɗe mbii ɗesǝ mo kyes, ɓe nghan naa nenlep kǝ Naan mo feer, moo ɗar nkoop kwang ɗefeer mǝ yil nǝ, mo yaa kut ɗin nkwang ɗefeer mǝ yil nǝ mo ɗar kǝ nǝ, mbǝkǝ taji mee kut cutpee nkaa yil nǝ, koo nkaa baahar, koo nkaa tǝng mo kas.
\v 2 Ɗangɓe nghan naa mee ngulep nNaan, ɗe wur kǝ put a nkoop puus kàa, wur kǝ me bii lǝlu Awas pee Naan ɗe kǝ seen nsar wur. Wur pet nenlep ɗefeer nǝ mo shi ɗoo ɗi ɓalɓal ɗe mo shin iiko mo, mbǝkǝ mo tǝkook kǝ yil kǝ am.
\v 3 Ɓe wur sat nǝnee, <<Taji wu wat yil nǝ, koo baahar nǝ, koo tǝng mo kas. Wu ɗar akuɗang, see mǝ le fili (alaama) mǝ lǝluwas mǝ Naan nkaa pǝkyeen mǝ kǝrem wur mo akuɗang.>>
\v 4 Ɗangɓe nghan kǝlǝng ɗuu nen ɗǝ mo le fili (alaama) nǝ mo mpǝkyeen mo, mo ngal kambil mǝndong kǝ lar feer baafeer. Nen ɗesǝ nǝ mo put a ndǝǝn koo soon ɗeɗangyi mǝ nen Izrel mo.
\q1 
\v 5 nKwang soon Juda mo, Ngal kaapaat baavǝl
\q1 nKwang soon mǝ Ruben mo, Ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\q2 nƊǝǝn soon mǝ Gad mo, Ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\q1 
\v 6 nKwang soon mǝ Asher mo, ngal kaapaat baavǝl,
\q1 nKwang soon mú Naftali mo, ngal kaapaat baavǝl,
\q2 nKwang soon Manasseh, ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\q1 
\v 7 nKwang soon mǝ Simiyon, ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\q1 nKwang soon Levayi mo, ngal kaapaat baavǝl,
\q2 nKwang soon Isaka, ngal kaapaat baavǝl,
\q1 nKwang soon Zebulum, ngal kaapaat baavǝl,
\q2 nKwang soon Josef, ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\q1 
\v 8 nKwang soon Zebulum, ngal kaapaat baavǝl,
\q1 nKwang soon Josef, ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\q2 nKwang soon mǝ Benjami mo, ngal kaapaat baavǝl.
\s1 Ɗuu Gurum mo kǝ nlǝr ɗepiyaa
\p 
\v 9 Aɓwoon ɗesǝ, ɓe wen ool, mbǝ ɗuu gurum mo ɗes, ɗe baa mee gurum mak tang mo kas. Nen ɗesǝ nǝ mo puwat a ndǝǝn yil mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ nkwang soon mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ gurum mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ liispwoo mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ ndǝǝn koo a pee ɗeɗangyi ndǝǝn yil ɗǝsǝ. Mo ɗar ntoom peetong mǝ mulki, kǝ ntoom Laatǝm. Mo jwal lée ɗepiyaa mo, mo kǝ kom kǝkar nsar mo zak.
\v 10 Mo ɗiyeep ɗoo mo mo ashak shiɓal, nǝnee,
\q1 <<Ɓam tong a pǝ Naan fun,
\q2 ɗe wur tong
\q1 nkaa peetong mǝ mulki sǝ,
\q1 kǝ Laatǝm nǝ.>>
\p 
\v 11 Nenlep mo jir, moo ɗar atǝng neer peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, kǝ nennan sǝ mo, kǝ mbǝ ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ mo zak. Nenlep nǝ mo saam kǝ yit fur nyil ntoom peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, kǝ mo seyil nNaan.
\v 12 Mo sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Nǝ aasǝ, kwoop, kǝ ɗehai, kǝ seen,
\q2 kǝ pǝlang, kǝ ɗǝɗes, kǝ iiko,
\q1 kǝ ɓal, mo ɗee a mǝ Naan fun
\q2 mbǝ ngaa-ngaa, Nǝ aasǝ.>>
\p 
\v 13 Ɗangɓe memee mɓut nennan nǝ mo wur tal pǝ an ɗi, ɓe wur sat nǝnee, <<Nen ɗǝ mo din nlǝr ɗe piyaa-piyaa sǝ mo awii mo me? Mo pwat a ni jii?>>
\p 
\v 14 Wen lap nwur nǝnee, <<Daa fen, a man.>>
\p Ɗangɓe wur sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Nen ɗesǝ mo, a nen
\q1 ɗe mo pwat ndǝǝn nen
\q2 ɗi mo shin keer mo,
\q1 mo kǝ vwang lée nmo,
\q1 kǝ mo ɗee a ɗepiyaa mo,
\q2 ndǝǝn toom Laatǝm.
\q1 
\v 15 A mpeemǝnǝ, ɓe moo ɗar ntoom peetong mǝ
\q2 mulki Naan,
\q1 kǝ moo seyil ndǝǝn Lu Naan ɗǝdes,
\q2 mpaar kǝ puus.
\q1 Gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa peetong
\q1 mǝ mulki nǝ,
\q2 wur tap mo.
\q1 
\v 16 Baa neen ncham láa mo kas,
\q2 kǝ zak, baa neen am cham tu mo kas.
\q1 Baa puus, koo tal
\q1 kǝ puus nǝn
\q2 cham mo kas.
\q1 
\v 17 Laatǝm ɗe wur nnaar
\q1 peetong mǝ mulki nǝ,
\q2 wur nɗeen a ngukiyeer mo.
\q1 Wur dǝm kǝ mo a pee tuɓut
\q2 ɗe nǝ a mǝ seen.
\q1 Naan wur mpwes
\q2 yitmwaan mo jir.>>
\c 8
\s1 Bii Lulwas ɗe pwoovǝl // ne kǝ Ɗaa Shool Zinaria.
\p 
\v 1 Ɗe Laatǝm nǝ fulep bii luwas ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ ɓe pee ɗok titik nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, mbe nǝ kus kǝ koor awa mǝndong.
\v 2 Wen naa jeplep Naan mo pwoovǝl, ɗe moo ɗar ntoom Naan, ɓe mo shin feer mo pwoovǝl.
\p 
\v 3 Mee ngulep Naan wur jì ɗar kus kǝ peewus mbiizuum, wur kǝ mee shool mǝ zinariya wus mbezuum. Mo shin mwoor ɗeɗu shangshang mǝ wus mbiizuum nwur ɗes, mbǝkǝ wur shin mo ɗe ashak kǝ ɗangnaan mǝ nen Naan mo, nkaa peewus mbiizuum ɗe mo ɗak nǝ a shi zinariya, ɗe nǝ ntoom peetong mǝ mulki ne.
\v 4 Ɗiyeel wus mbezuum ɗǝ kǝ toos shangshang nǝ, kǝ ɗangnaan mǝ nen Naan mo, ɗe nǝn nsar ngulep Naan nǝ, nǝ kàa wul pee Naan ɗǝ.
\v 5 Ɗangɓe ngulep nǝ wur mang ɗaa shool mǝ wus mbezuum nǝ, wur gam shool nǝ shi wus nkaa pe wus mbiizuum nǝ, ɓe wur vwet nkaa yil nǝ, Kaaɗe wur vwet wus ɗesǝ nǝ nkaa yil nǝ, ɓe peekwoot, kǝ ɗoo mo, kǝ pee mǝlep, ɓe yil nǝ yoon.
\s1 Feer nǝ mo
\p 
\v 6 Ɓe nenlep Naan ɗepwoovǝl ɗe mo kǝ feer mo pwoovǝl sǝ, mo ɗaksut, mbǝkǝ mo tàa feer nǝ mo.
\p 
\v 7 Ngulep Naan ɗinshee tàa feer wur, ɓe ɗoor kǝ wus, riyeep kǝ toom, mo sham ɓeer nkaa yil nǝ. Mǝndong nkaa kun, mǝ yil nǝ caan, kǝ mǝndong nkaa kun mǝ tǝng mo caan zak, kǝ shit ɗe mbrak mo caan jir.
\p 
\v 8 Ngulep Naan ɗevǝl tàa feer wur, ɓe mee mbii kaa duum jwak lap wus, ɓe mo vwet nǝ ndǝǝn baahar. Mǝndong nkaa kun mǝ baahar nǝ cǝǝr atoom.
\v 9 Ɓe Mǝndong nkaa kun, mǝ mbǝɗe mo kǝ seen ɗen baahar nǝ mo murep jir, Mǝndong nkaa kun, mǝ tii mo tǝkook.
\p 
\v 10 Ngulep Naan ɗekun wur tàa feer wur, ɓe mee zar ɗǝɗes, ɗe nǝ lap wus hǝlak-hǝlak kaa ngǝyem sǝ, nǝ put aɗeng ɓe nǝ sham táa nkaa mǝndong mɓut nkun, mǝ gyeen mo, kǝ tuɓut mǝ am mo.
\v 11 Sǝm zar ɗesǝ nǝ a, Ɗeet. Ɓe mǝndong mɓut nkun mǝ am nǝ, mo cǝǝr ɗee a ɗeɗeet, gurum mo ɗes mo murep, mbǝ am ɗǝ nǝ kǝ ɗen a ɗeɗeet.
\p 
\v 12 Ngulep Naan ɗefeer tàa feer wur, ɓe mo cut mǝndong mɓut nkun mǝ puus, kǝ mǝndong mɓut nkun mǝ tar, kǝ mǝndong mɓut nkun mǝ zar mo, Mɓemǝnǝ, ɓe mǝndong mɓut nkun mǝ peeɓang mo baa moo kuɗi kǝ ɓangpee kas. Mǝndong mɓut nkun mǝ puus, baa nǝ kuɗi kǝ peeɓang kas, kǝ mǝndong ɗin kun mǝ paar nǝ ɓangpee kas.
\p 
\v 13 Kaaɗe nghan naapee, ɓe nghan kǝlǝng mee puul, ɗe nǝ mwaan aɗeng, nii petpee shi ɗoo ɗeɓal, nǝnee, <<Jeel! Jeel! Jeel. Mpee gurum ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil nǝ, mbǝɗe nenlep Naan ɗe mo kuɗi kun sǝ, mo kus kǝ tàa feer mo.>>
\c 9
\p 
\v 1 Ngulep Naan ɗepaat wur tàa feer wur, ɓe nghan naa mee zar ɗe nǝ tong a ɗengnan sham taa ɓǝm-yil nǝ. Mo shin biwangpee nzar nǝ mǝ tuun ɗejurum, ɗe baa nǝ kǝ peeɗar sǝ kas nwur.
\v 2 Kaaɗe wur wang pwoo tuun ɗejurum ɗesǝ nǝ, ɓe ɗyeel kàa put ndǝǝn tuun nǝ, kaa ɗyeel wus ɗe nǝ se lu sǝ. Ɗiyeel ɗesǝ nǝ kàa paa puus, kǝ ɗengnaan, mbe pee nǝ rap kaa par sǝ.
\v 3 nƊǝǝn ɗyeel ɗesǝ nǝ, ɓe ciɓel mo sham nkaa yil nǝ, mo shín ɓal mo kaa mǝ ɗoor mo sǝ.
\v 4 Mo sat mo, << taji wu tung shit, koo tǝng, kǝ bii ɗǝ mo kop mo ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil nǝ kas, mɓe wu tung a nen ɗe baa mo kǝ mbii luwas mǝ Naan pǝkyeen mo kas.
\v 5 Baa mo shin iiko nǝ mo a mbǝkǝ mo twe nen ɗesǝ nǝ mo kas, mɓe mo shin iiko nǝ mo, a mbǝkǝ mo shinjeel ɗe nen ɗesǝ nǝ mo mbǝ tar mo paat. Jeel ɗe mo shwaa nǝ, nǝ shwal kaa shwal ɗe ɗoor pus gurum sǝ.
\v 6 nƊǝǝn tar ɗepaat ɗesǝ nǝ mo, ɓe nen ɗesǝ nǝ mo yap muut, mɓe baa mo kat kas. Moo rǝɓet muut mɓe muut nǝ dǝm jong kǝ mo.
\p 
\v 7 Ciɓel ɗesǝ nǝ mo lapshak kǝ bǝring ɗe mo tap ɗak mo mbǝ dǝm nlek. Mo jwal mee mbii mo nkáa mo, kaa mbiikáa ɗe mo ɗak mo shi zinariya sǝ, kǝ zak, yit mo lapshak kǝ yit ngurum mo.
\v 8 Shwepkáa mo, a kaa mǝ shurep mo sǝ, kǝ zak, oos mo nǝ a kaa oos mǝ mbwoor mo sǝ.
\v 9 Mo paa tuur mo nǝ mo, shi shool, kǝ cáap mo mo wal nciit kǝ wal mǝ shii bǝring ɗe moo dul keke bǝring mo mbǝ dǝm nlek.
\v 10 Mo kǝ nɗang ɗe nii pwaspee kaa ɗoor mo sǝ. A shi ndang ɗesǝ mo, ɓe mo katɓal mbǝ shinjeel gurum mo, mbǝ tar mo paat.
\v 11 Mo kǝ gwe ɗǝ a kaa mishkoom mo a ngulep mǝ tuun ɗejurum, ɗe baa nǝ kǝ peeɗar kas sǝ, sǝm wur shi Yahudi, a Abaaddon, ɗangɓe sǝm wur shi Heleni a Apoliyon. Shi mǝnǝ a nǝnee, <<Ngutǝkook kǝ mbii mo.>>
\p 
\v 12 Jeel ɗeɗes ɗinshee nǝ ɗel mmǝnǝ. Ɗee jeel ɗeɗes mo ɗe vǝl, ɗe mo ndang jì.
\p 
\v 13 Ngulep kǝ Naan ɗepeemee nǝ wur tàa feer wur, ɗangɓe nghan kǝlǝng mee ɗoo nǝ jì put ndǝǝn kwang ɗefeer mǝ peewus mbezuum ɗe mo ɗak nǝ a shi zinariya, ɗe nǝ ɗar ntoom Naan.
\v 14 Ɗoo nǝ katpwoo ngulep ɗepeemee ɗǝ wur kǝ feer nǝ nǝ nǝnee, <<A fween nenlep ɗefeer sǝ mo, ɗe gyet mo ɓwoot mo le ngǝyen Yufrates ɗeɗes sǝ.>>
\v 15 Nenlep ɗefeer ɗesǝ mo, mo gyet bwet mo a mbe pee ɗesǝ, kǝ teer, kǝ tar, kǝ ɓit nǝ, gyet mo ɓwet mo, kǝ mo twe gurum ɗe nyil nǝ mo mǝndong kaa kun.
\v 16 Ɗuu shiiton ɗe mo lang bǝring nǝ mo a miliyon kambil vǝl. Wen kǝlǝng ɗuu mo nǝ
\p 
\v 17 Bǝring nǝ mo kǝ nenlang nǝ mo, ɗe wen naa mo ndǝǝn suun fen nǝ, mo lap kǝsǝ, gwat tuur mo, ɗe nǝ naat kaa wus sǝ, nǝ tǝp kaa ɗengnaan sǝ, kǝ zak, nǝ a kaa fwat wus sǝ. Káa bǝring nǝ mo lapshak kǝ mǝ nvar mo. Wus kǝ ɗiyeel, kǝ fwat wus mo jì put mpwoo kǝ bǝring nǝ mo.
\v 18 Mǝnɗong kaa kun mǝ gurum ɗe nyil nǝ mo mo murep mbe mbii shin jeel ɗekun ɗesǝ mo, wus nǝ, kǝ ɗiyeel, kǝ fwat wus ɗe pwat pwoo bǝring nǝ mo.
\v 19 Ɓal bǝring nǝ mo, a nɗǝǝn pwoo mo, kǝ ndang mo mo. Dang mo nǝ mo a kaa nwòo mo sǝ, ɗe mo kǝ káa. A shi nɗang ɗesǝ nǝ mo, ɓe bǝring ɗesǝ mo cínjeel gurum ɗe nyil mo.
\p 
\v 20 Kaar gurum ɗe baa mo murǝp nsar kǝ jeel ɗesǝ mo kas, ɓe baa mo tuwap kas, mo sat a nseyil nriin ɗebish mo, kǝ kùm ɗe mo ɗak shi zinariya, kǝ azurfa, kǝ bòng ɗenaat, kǝ jwak, kǝ yoom mo. Baa moo naapee, koo kǝlǝngpee, koo mee mwaan kas.
\v 21 Baa mo waa tuwap mbǝ tukáa ɗe moo cin nǝ kas, kǝ mulak, mo kǝ shin ngaa, kǝ wat.
\c 10
\s1 Laalepnaan kǝ Rep Laa Garvit
\p 
\v 1 Ɗangɓe wen naa mee ngulep kǝ Naan ɗeɗes, wur tong a ɗengnaan sham. nLuu paa wur kaa nlǝr sǝ, kǝ zak, wiw neer káa wur cǝǝrkaat. Yit wur nǝ a kaa puus sǝ, kǝ shii wur nǝ mo a kaa ndwet ɗǝnan-nan mǝ wus sǝ.
\v 2 Wur kǝ mee replàa garvit, ɗe nǝ a wuwang nsar wur, wur leshii se wur nǝ nkaa baahar, kǝ shii kul wur nǝ kaa yil,
\v 3 Ɗangɓe wur petpee shi ɗoo ɗeɓal ɗe nǝ lap shak kǝ or mǝ nvar. Kaaɗe wur kǝ petpee nǝ, ɓe peekwoot ɗepwoovǝl mo lap nwur shi ɗoo ɗeɓal.
\v 4 Kaaɗe peekwoot ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo leshap, ɓe wen kǝn rǝɓet ran nǝ, mɓe wen kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ndǝǝn ɗengnaan sat nǝnee, <<A shoot mbǝɗe nluu ɗe mo petpee pwoovǝl nǝ mo sat. Taji a ran mbǝɗe mo sat nǝ kas.>>
\p 
\v 5 Ɗangɓe ngulep kǝ Naan, ɗe mee shii wur nǝ nkaa baahar, kǝ mee shii wur nkaa yil sǝ, wur ɗiyeep sar se wur kaa aɗeng.
\v 6 Wur tuceerpwoo nɗǝǝn sǝm kǝ Naan ɗe wur ɗe ngaa-ngaa, Wur ɗe wur le ɗengnaan ke mbii ɗe ɗǝǝn mo, kǝ ɓǝm-yil kǝ mbii ɗe ɗǝǝn mo, kǝ baahar kǝ mbii ɗe ɗǝǝn mo. Laalep nNaan nǝ sat nǝ, <<Baa mee pee kuɗi kas!
\v 7 Katɗang laalep Naan ɗe pwoovǝl wur kus tàa feer wur nǝ, ɓe mbii mǝ Naan ɗesǝsok mo ngam, kaaɗe gyet wur kǝ ten sat nkǝrem wur mo, nensatpwoo Naan mo.
\p 
\v 8 ɗangɓe ɗoo ɗe ken kǝlǝn sǝ nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, nǝ katpwoo kǝ nghan zak nǝnee, <<A dǝm, a mang ngarvit ɗe wuwang nsar laalep nNaan ɗe wur kǝ ɗar nkaa baahar kǝ yil.>>
\p 
\v 9 nƊǝm pee Laalep nNaan nǝ ntal kǝ wur shin rep laagarvit nǝ nghan. Wur sat nghan nǝ, <<A la, a se. Nǝ be nɗuwang ɓut nfwaa, dang mɓut mpwoo fwaa, ɓe nǝn mbǝ shang kaa loor nshii sǝ.>>
\v 10 Wen la replàa ngarvit nǝn nsar Laalep nǝ nse, ɓe nǝ shang nciit kǝ loor nshii pwoo fen. Abwoon ɗe nɗal nǝ, mɓe cǝǝr ɗuwang ɗuwaan mɓut fen.
\v 11 Ɗangɓe mo sat nghan nǝnee, <<Nǝ atǝng a baa can joom zak ɗǝ gurum mo shinǝ-shinǝ kǝ nyil mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ lespwoo mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ nkaa mishkoom mo mo shinǝ-shinǝ zak.>>
\c 11
\s1 Nensatpwoo Ɗevǝl Mo
\p 
\v 1 nLa mee kam, kaa kám kam mbii sǝ, ɗangɓe mo sat nghan nǝnee, <<A dǝm a kám Lu Naan ɗeɗes nǝ, kǝ peewus mbezuum nǝ kǝ, a tang ɗuu nen seyil nǝ mo.
\v 2 Mbe taji a kám fuur nǝ kas, mbǝɗe mo kǝ ten shin mǝnǝ, nen ɗe baa mo a nen Yahudi mo kas. Nen ɗesǝ mon treng nkaa yilkaam ɗeɓang nǝ, mbǝ tar mo laarfeer baavǝl.
\v 3 Wen mbe nshin nlangtǝng fen mo vǝl, mbǝkǝ mo sat joom, mbǝ teer mo ngal mǝndong kǝ ɗari vǝl kǝ laarpeemee. Mo njwal leemaap mo.>>
\p 
\v 4 Nenlangtǝng ɗevǝl ɗesǝ nǝ mo, a mo a tingpaat ɗevǝl sǝ mo, kǝ ngyem ɗevǝl sǝ mo zak, ɗe moo ɗar ntoom kǝ Daa ɗe mǝ yil ɗesǝ ne.
\v 5 Katɗang mee gurum kǝ rǝɓet tǝkook kǝ mo, ɓe wus njì put mpwoo mo, mbe nǝ se shaarlek mo mo. A ɗesǝ ɗee, a ar muut jir gwar ɗe wur kǝ rǝɓet tǝtook kǝ mo ating kǝ wur muut.
\v 6 Nen ɗesǝ nǝ mo kǝ iiko, mbǝkǝ mo shoot ɗengnaan, mbǝkǝ taji fwan jì kas, nɗǝǝn teer ɗe mo nkaa can joom. Kǝzak, mo kǝ iiko, mbǝkǝ mo le am mo jir, mo ceer a toom. Mo mak cut mɓǝmyil nǝ shi shwal mo shini-shini, kaaɗe mo naa nǝ ret mo nyit sǝ.
\p 
\v 7 Aɓwoon ɗe mo nkyes sat caamkat mo nǝ mo, ɓe mee luwa ɗe nǝ kàa put nɗǝǝn tuun ɗe baa nǝ kǝ peeɗar kas sǝ. Luwa ɗesǝ nǝn mɓwet lek nkaa mo, mbe nǝn nse koorong nkaa mo, ɗangɓe nǝn ntwe mo zak.
\v 8 Kúm ɗes nǝ mo mbǝ ngǝrang nɗǝǝn peekat mǝ yilkaam ɗǝnan-nan sǝ mo, ɗe moo kǝ koon mo a kǝ <<Sodom>> kǝ <<Ijip>> sǝ, pee ɗe gyet mo pwas Daa mo ɗe.
\v 9 Mbe teer kun kǝ koor ɓǝ Gurum, mo shinǝ-shinǝ, soon mo shinǝ-shinǝ, liispwoo mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ yil shinǝ-shinǝ, mo nnaa kúm kǝ mo nǝ, mbǝ mo ncii wum kúm kǝ mo ne.
\v 10 Nen ɗe moo tong nɗǝǝn yil ɗese, mo mbe ncìn retnyit mbǝ murǝp kǝ das ɗevǝl ɗesǝ nǝ mo, mo mbe yool mǝrep kǝ retyit. Kǝ zak, mo nlep zuum mo nshak, mbǝɗe nenjoom ɗe ɗevǝl sǝ mo kǝ shinjeel nen ɗe yil nǝ mo.
\p 
\v 11 Aɓwoon teer mo kun kǝ koor, ɓe Naan wur le kǝ nook mǝ seen ɗel nɗǝǝn mo, mbe mo yool ɗar nkaa shii mo mo, ɗangɓe mee kǝǝrmuut ɗeɗes nǝ yaa nen ɗe mo naa mo.
\v 12 Ɗangɓe nen ɗevǝl sǝ mo kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ɗeɗes ɗe nǝ put nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan nǝ sat mo nǝnee, <<Wu kàa sǝ.>> Ɓe shaarlek mo naa mo ɗel kàa nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan ɗǝǝn nluu.
\p 
\v 13 Abet-abet, ɓe yil nǝ yoon ɓalɓal. Mǝndong mɓut nkaapaat mǝ yil nǝ pyan, kǝ gurum mo ngal pwoovǝl, mo murǝp nɗǝǝn yoon kǝ yil mǝnǝ. Kǝǝrmuut ɗeɗes yaa koor nen ɗe mo baar nǝ mo, mbe mo kwoop ɗǝdes nNaan ɗe wur nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan.
\p 
\v 14 Aɓwoon mbii shin keermuut ɗevǝl kǝ ɗel, mɓe mbii shin keermuut ɗekun nǝn njì kǝlak-kǝlak.
\s1 Feer Ɗe pwoovǝl
\p 
\v 15 Ngulep Naan ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ wur tàa feer fǝn, ɓe ɗoo ɗeɓal-ɓal mo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, mo sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Semishkoom mǝ yil ɗesǝ nǝ,
\q2 nǝ ɗee a mulki mǝ Daa fun,
\q1 kǝ mǝ Kristi,
\q2 wur ncìn mulki nǝ a mbǝ ngaa-ngaa.>>
\p 
\v 16 Ɗangɓe nennan ɗe Laarvǝl baafeer sǝ mo, ɗe moo tong nkaa mbii tong mǝ mulki mo mo ntoom kǝ Naan sǝ, mo kurum nyil, kǝ mo seyil ɗe nNaan.
\v 17 Mo sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Mu pǝlang waa, Daa Naan ɗeɓal met jir,
\q1 A waa ɗe yaksǝ, kǝ ɗe ɗeyaam,
\q2 mɓeeɗe aa mang iiko fwa
\q1 ɗeɗes,
\q2 kǝ a yaa se mulki.
\q1 
\v 18 Yil nǝ mo langtuup,
\q2 dang tuurnung ɗebish ɓish fwaa kǝ ji.
\q1 Pee nǝ wul ɗe mon
\q1 tokɗyeel Nen mumuut mo,
\q2 kǝ shin kwat
\q1 kerǝm fwaa nen cin joom mo
\q1 kǝ nen fwaa mo
\q2 ɗe moo ɗyeep sǝm fwaa,
\q1 ɗenan, kǝ ɗeɗyeen
\q1 kǝ mbe tǝkook kǝ nen ɗe mo
\q2 tǝkook kǝ ɓǝmyil nǝ.>>
\p 
\v 19 Lu Naan ɗeɗes ɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan wang, ɓe mo naa Kwati Mǝ Tucǝǝrpwoo shi toom mǝ Naan. Ɗangɓe pee nǝ mǝlep ɗes, kǝ ɗoo ɗeɗes mo, mǝ peekwoot, ɓe yil nǝ yoon, kǝ vivir.
\c 12
\s1 mat kǝ nwòo
\p 
\v 1 Mee mbii naaman ɗeɗes put ɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, Mee mat war, lep nlǝr puus, kǝ tar nder shii war, kǝ war lepmbiikaa mulki kǝ zar mo kaapaat baavǝl nkáa war.
\v 2 War dǝ kǝ aak ɓe war wal ɗeɓal ɓut shal, kaaɗe aak nǝ ɗoom se war.
\v 3 Ɗangɓe mee mbii naaman zak nǝ jì put ɗe nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan nǝ, mee duum nwòo ɗeɗes, ɗe nǝ a naat, kǝ káa mo pwoovǝl, kǝ soom mo kaapaat, kǝ mbiikáa mǝ mulki mo pwoovǝl, nkaa nǝ.
\v 4 nƊang nwòo nǝ fet mǝndong kaa nkun, mǝ zar ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan sham ɗyong nyil. Nwòo nǝ ɗar akyeen mat ɗe war pǝ yap làa-làa sǝ, mbǝkǝ nǝ ɓalapǝ se làa nǝ ɗi kaɗang war laa.
\v 5 War làa ɗemish, wur ɓe nse mulki nkaa nyil mo jir, shi kamshool. Nǝ ɓam laa nǝ kwet! Shi kàa pee Naan ɗi, npeetong mulki wur.
\v 6 Mat nǝ war su dǝm a naaryil, a npeeɗe Naan wur tap ɗakle nwar, ɗe mo ntap war, mbe teer mo ngal mǝndong, kǝ kambil vǝl kǝ laarpeemee.
\p 
\v 7 Lek yool nɗǝǝn nɗengnaan. Makiyel kǝ nenlep wur mo, mo nkaa lek kǝ nwòo nǝ, nwoo nǝ kǝ nenlep wur mo cǝǝr lek kǝ mo.
\v 8 Dang baa ɓal wur nǝ mak kas ɓe mo ceen wur ɗǝǝn ɗengNaan nǝ.
\v 9 Mo mang cut am ɗesǝ nǝ, mo vwet wur shin sham nɗǝǝn yil nǝ nwòo ɗegyet mǝnǝ mo pet wur a ngujwaan, ko shetan ɗǝ wur gwom gurum mo yil nǝ dǝm kǝnǝ a ar ɗe nkan mo mang wur vwet shi sham yil, kǝ jeplep wur mo.
\v 10 Ɗangɓe nghan kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ɗeɗes nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan nǝ sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Yaksǝ, ɓe ɓam Naan nǝ kǝ njì wul,
\q1 kǝ iiko
\q2 kǝ mulki mǝ Naan fun, kǝ iiko mǝ kristi.
\q1 Ɓe gwar ɗe wur fǝlǝp ɗyemnǝǝn fun mo,
\q1 ntoom Naan fun
\q2 puus kǝ par
\q1 mo vwet shin sham yil.
\q1 
\v 11 Mo se koorong nkaa wur
\q2 mbǝ toom kǝ
\q1 Laatǝm kǝ,
\q2 pwoo kaa caamkat mo,
\q1 baa mo wal
\q2 seen fur kas
\q1 hakyeng
\q2 ɓe mo shin seen fur har muut.
\q1 
\v 12 Mɓemǝnǝ, ɓe wu cin retnyit, wun ɗengnaan mo,
\q1 <<kǝ nen ɗe moo
\q2 tong nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan nǝ mo zak,
\q1 Mbe jeel kaa ɓǝmyil,
\q2 kǝ baahar nǝ,
\q1 mɓeeɗe ngujwaan
\q1 wur kǝ sham pee wun ɗi,
\q2 Wur gam kǝ pǝtuup ɗewat,
\q1 Wur man pee
\q2 wur nǝ ɗee a lee ɗak.>>
\p 
\v 13 Kaaɗe cut am ɗesǝ nǝ naa, nǝ, mo vwet wuɗin shin sham nɗǝǝn yil ɗese, ɓe nǝ yaa sushii nɗang mat ɗe war làa-làa ɗemish sǝ.
\v 14 Mbe mo shin cáap mat nǝ mo vǝl ɗe ɗǝnan-nan mǝ puul, mbǝkǝ war katpee yool dǝm wul pee ɗe mo kǝ ten ɗak war annaar yil, pee ɗe mo mbe tap war ɗe ɓǝrepee, kǝ koor pee ɗe baa nwoo nǝ mak wul ɗe kas.
\v 15 Ɗangɓe Nwòo nǝ wuut am shin put mpwoo nǝ kaa gyeen sǝ, ɓe kǝ am nǝ ɗel mat nǝ kǝ nǝ soo war seet kǝ nǝ kǝ tungzung nǝ.
\v 16 Ɗangɓe yil nǝ ɓam mat nǝ war, ɓe nǝ wang pwoo nǝ ɓe nǝ ɗal gyeen ɗe cut am nǝ wuut pwoo wur nǝ.
\v 17 Tuup fes tu nwòo nǝ nɗang mat war kaaɗe nǝ naa baa nǝ mak yaa mat nǝ war kas, ɓe nǝ dǝm yaa lek nkaa ndang kǝ war nǝ mo. Dang kǝ mat nǝ, a nen ɗe moo kǝlǝng ɗoo kǝ Naan, ɗe mo kǝ caamkat kǝ Jesu.
\v 18 kut am nǝ ɗar nkaa pwoo ɗyees mǝ am baahar ne.
\c 13
\s1 Luwayil mo vǝl
\p 
\v 1 nWoo, nǝ ɗar duk ɗyees kǝ pwoo am baahar ɓe nnaa mee Luwayil kǝ put ɗǝǝn am baahar. nǝ kǝ soom mo kaapaat, kǝ káa mo pwoovǝl, nǝ kǝ mbiikáa mǝ mulki mo kaapaat nkaa soom wur nǝ mo, koo a káa ɗeɗang yii, ɓe mo ran mee sǝm ɗe nǝ satpwoo ɗebish.
\v 2 Luwayil ɗe nghan naa nǝ, nǝ lapshak kǝ lushim, ɗang nǝ kǝ shii kaa mǝ ludang kǝ pwoo nǝ kaa mǝ nvar sǝ nwoo nǝ shin ɓal fen luwayil kǝ peetong mulki wur nǝ kǝ iiko Ɗeɓal.
\v 3 Mee ɓut káa wur nǝ mo nciit kǝ nǝ mee laa ɗebish bish ɗang laa ɗebish-bish nǝ kǝ zuum. Yil nǝ gam kǝ mbii aapwoo ɓe nǝ taadang Luwayil nǝ.
\v 4 Gurum mo seyil nwoo nǝ ɓeeɗe nǝ shin iikoo luwayil nǝ, ɗang ɓe mo seyil nluwayil nǝ ɓe mo tal nǝnee <<A wee kaa luwayil nǝ sǝ? A wee mak cin lek kǝ nǝ yii?>>
\p 
\v 5 Mo shin pwoo nluwa ɗesǝ nǝ mbe kǝ nǝ satpwoo roop, kǝ moo fǝlǝp Naan ɗe kǝ nǝ cin ɗak kǝ iikoo fǝn ɗi mbǝ tar mo laarfeer baavǝl.
\v 6 Luwa nǝ wang pwoo nǝ mbe kǝ nǝ satpwoo ɗebuu mo kaa Naan, kǝ nǝ tǝkook kǝ sǝm wur ɗi kǝ peetong wur, kǝ des ɗi mo kǝ tong a Ɗengnan
\v 7 Mo Shin ɓal nǝ mbǝkǝ nǝ cin lek ɗe nkaa nen Naan ɗeɓang mo kǝ se koorong kaa mo. Ɗang mo shin iiko nkaa jir soon ɗeɗang yii, gurum ɗeɗang yii, liispwoo ɗeɗang yii? kǝ yil ɗǝɗang yi.
\v 8 Jir nǝn ɗe moo kǝ tong nɗǝǝn ɓǝmyil ɗesǝ mo ɓe seyil luwayil nǝ. Jir sǝm ɗi baa mo kǝ ran mo ɗǝǝn bǝǝthaal mǝ seen mǝ laatǝm, laatǝm ɗǝ di mo tuu pǝ gyet ɗe nshee kǝ yil nǝ.
\q1 
\v 9 Ngwe ɗe wur kǝ kom
\q2 mbǝ kǝlǝngpee.
\q1 <<
\v 10 Katɗang mee gurum
\q1 bǝ dǝm pee shoot,
\q2 ɓe moo dǝm kǝ wur peeshoot.
\q1 Katɗang mo
\q2 ntu mee gwe a shi kwai,
\q1 ɓe nǝ a tǝng mo ntu wur
\q2 a shi kwai nǝ.>>
\p Ɗesǝ nǝ a petpee mbǝkǝ mo gung, kǝ mo ɗar ɗe ɓalɓal kǝ shinzeen nkwang nen Naan mo.
\s1 Luwa Yil Ɗe Put mɓǝmyil Nǝ
\p 
\v 11 Ɗangɓe naa mee luwayil ɗevǝl, ɗǝ nii put ɗǝǝn Ɓǝmyil. Luwa ɗesǝ nǝ kǝ soom mo vǝl kaa laatǝm sǝ, Mbe nǝ leeshap kaa kut am sǝ.
\v 12 Luwa ɗesǝ nǝ cin ɗak kǝ iiko mǝ luwayil ɗeshee nǝ koppee nǝ, kǝ nǝ lee ɓǝmyilɗ kǝ mbii ɗe kǝ tong ɗǝǝn mo seyil ɗe luwayil ɗeshee nǝ, ɗe laa nǝ ɗebish bish sǝ kǝ zuum.
\v 13 Luwayil ɗevǝl ɗesǝ nǝ cin mbii nnaaman mo ɗes hakyeng, nǝ le kǝ wus tong aɗeng Naan sham nkaa ɓǝmyil nǝ nyitnaapee gurum mo.
\v 14 Mbee mbii nnaaman nǝ mo ɓe mo shin ɓal nǝ ɓe cin mbii mo koo-pee mǝ luwayil ɗe nshee nǝ, nǝ gwam nen tong ɗǝǝn ɓǝm-yil nǝ mo. wur lee mo mo ɗen mbii kum mo ɓut shin ɗǝdes luwayil ɗe ɗi wur kat laa shi kwai jir kǝsǝ ɓe wur kǝ seen.
\v 15 Mo shínɓal nluwayil ɗevǝl kǝ wur shin nook ɗe kum luwayil ɗinshee nǝ, kǝ kum nǝ leeshaap ɗi kǝ wur lee jir ngwe ɗi wur cii seyil kum nǝ ɓe mo tu.
\v 16 Nǝ lee ting gurum mo jir, ɗeɗes kǝ ɗelee, nenlong, kǝ nenjeel, jeplu mo, kǝ kǝrem mo, kǝ mo lap mee mbiinaaman nkaa sarse mo, koo nkaa pǝkyeen mo mo,
\v 17 Kǝ taji mo mak seet koo seet kǝ mbii kas see mo kǝ mbii naaman ɗese, ɗe nǝ a sǝm luwayil mǝne koo mee lambaa ɗe naa sǝm nǝ.
\p 
\v 18 Ɗese nǝ wal a seen ɓe see a ngwe ɗe wur kǝ seen, yit gwe ɗe wur kǝ ɗyeen wur yakshii luwayil nǝ mo ɗe, Mɓeɗe nǝ a lambaa mǝ gurum ɓe lambaa nǝ a 666.
\c 14
\s1 Laatǝm kǝ Gurum Mo 144,000
\p 
\v 1 Kaaɗe wen ɗiyeep yit, ɓe wen naa Laatǝm akyeen fen, wur ɗar nkaa jwak nZayon, ashak kǝ nen wur gurum, ɗe mo wul ngal kambil mǝndong kǝ laarfeer baafeer (144,000). Das ɗesǝ nǝ mo kǝ sǝm Laatǝm nǝ, kǝ sǝm kǝ puun wur a rǝran nkaa pǝkyeen mo jir.
\v 2 Ɗangɓe wen kǝlǝng mee ɗoo sǝ nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, ɗe nǝ nciit-nciit kǝ wal kǝ am ɗe nǝ sham nɗang ɗes, kǝ nǝ wal kaa peekwoot sǝ. Ɗoo ɗe kǝleng nǝ, nǝ a kaa nen ɗe mo pǝ taa nɗeng-nɗeng sǝ.
\v 3 Mo cin kook ɗepwoo ntoom kǝ mpeetong mǝ mulki nǝ, kǝ ntoom kǝ mbii ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ mo, kǝ ntoom kǝ nennan sǝ mo. Baa mee ngwe mak kám kook mǝnǝ kas, see a das ɗe mo ngal kambil mǝndong kǝ laarfeer baafeer. A mo a nen ɗe mo kǝ ten ang mo nɗǝǝn yil nǝ.
\v 4 Das ɗesǝ nǝ mo a nen ɗe baa gyet mo cam tǝkook kǝ sut kǝ mat mo kas, moo cam man mee mat mo kas. Mo dǝm nɗang Laatǝm nǝ, koo a pee ɗeɗang yii. Mo ang mo mɓut gurum mo, kǝ mo shin mo kaa laa tǝng ɗeshee nǝ nNaan, kǝ Laatǝm nǝ.
\v 5 Baa mee ɗung cam put mpwoo mo kas, mbǝɗe baa mo kǝ mee shikbish kas.
\s1 Jeplep-Naan mo kun
\p 
\v 6 Ɗangɓe wen naa mee ngulep Naan pwoo, nkaa mwaan nɗǝǝn kut a shi cáap, wur kǝ pwoo ɗeret, ɗeɗǝm ngaa-ngaa, Mbǝkǝ wur sat nǝ ɗe nen ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɓǝm-yil ɗese. Pwoo ɗesǝ nǝ, nǝ a mbǝ koo a yil ɗeɗang yii, kǝ mbǝ koo a soon ɗeɗang yii, koo a lespwoo ɗeɗang yii, kǝ nǝ a mbǝ gurum mo.
\v 7 Wur sat shi ɗoo ɗeɗes nǝnee, <<Wu kǝǝr Naan, wu cin ɗeɗes nwur, mbǝɗe puus tokɗyeel wur nǝ jì wul. Wu seyil nNaan, mbǝɗe a wur le ɗeng mo kǝ yil nǝ. A wur le am nɗǝǝn baahar, kǝ tuɓut mo zak.>>
\p 
\v 8 nGulep Naan ɗevǝl nǝ, jì sat nǝnee, << pal! Pal!! Yil Babilon ɗeɗes nǝ pal!!!. Gyet a war le ɗang gurum ɗe nɗǝǝn yil nǝ mo shinǝ-shinǝ mo shwaa am yuurpee, ɗe nǝ a mǝ cin ngaa.>>
\p 
\v 9 Mee ngulep Naan ɗekun wur taa dang mo, wur sat shi ɗoo ɗeɓal nǝnee, << Katɗang mee gurum seyil nluwayil sǝ, kǝ muriin wur, mbe kǝ ngwe mǝnǝ lap mbiinaaman mǝ luwayil nǝ nkaa pǝkyeen wur koo sar wur,
\v 10 Mo jir ɓe nshwaa am laa ting ɗe mǝ tuup Naan, Ɗi wur kǝ ten ɗoo shiɓal nɗǝǝn ɗaa shool wur ɗe nǝ a mǝ tuup wur. Mo nshínjeel ngwar mǝnǝ shi wus ɗenaat, ntoom jeplep-Naan ɗeɓang mo, kǝ Laatǝm ne.
\v 11 Ɗangɓe dyeel mǝ shwaajeel kǝ das mǝnǝ mo, nǝ yool kaa aɗeng mbǝ ngaa-ngaa. Baa mee nookɗi ɗi kas par kǝ puus ɓe nen ɗe mo seyil nluwayil kǝ mǝ riin nǝ, Kǝ koo aweyi ɗe la mbiinaaman mǝ sǝm ne.>>
\v 12 Ɗesǝ petpee nen Naan mo, mbǝkǝ mo gung ɗe ndǝǝn tap kǝ Wàar Naan, kǝ zak, mbǝkǝ mo ɗar ɗe ɓalɓal shi shinzeen mo nɗǝǝn Jesu.
\p 
\v 13 Ɗangɓe wen kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ndǝǝn ɗengnaan, nǝ sat nǝnee, <<A ran ɗesǝ, Ɗeret aa nen ɗe mo kǝ murep, nen ɗe mo mmurǝp ɗǝǝn Daa, yool nyaksǝ. ɗel dǝm akyeen>> Riin nǝ sat nǝ, << Ii, <<mo nnookɗi mɓut nɗak mo mo, mbǝɗe ɗak cin mo nǝ dǝm nɗang mo.>>
\s1 Ɗyip Ɓǝm-yil nǝ
\p 
\v 14 Naapee, akyeen fen, ɓe wen naa mee nluu ɗepiyaa, mee gwar kǝtong nkaa nluu nǝ, ɗe wur lapshak kǝ Làa Gurum. Wur kǝ mbiikáa mǝ zinariya nkaa káa wur, ɗǝ wur kǝ mee jeem ɗesese nsar wur.
\v 15 Ɓe mee ngulep-Naan wur jì put ndǝǝn Lu Naan ɗǝɗes, ɓe wur petpee gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa nluu sǝ, shi ɗoo ɗeɓal, <<A mang jeem fwa nǝ, kǝ a yaa ɗiip-ɗiip ɗe, mbǝɗe pee mǝ ɗiip nǝ kǝ jì wul, ɓedǝ Ɗǝɓen nǝ kǝ nung mak ɗiip.>>
\v 16 Gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa nluu sǝ, wur wiit jeem wur nkaa maar ɗe mo nɗǝǝn ɓǝmyil nǝ, ɓe mo ɗiip ɓǝm-yil nǝ.
\p 
\v 17 Mee ngulep Naan, wur jì put ndǝǝn Lu Naan ɗeɗes nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, ngulep ɗesǝ wur kǝ jeem ɗesese nsar wur zak.
\v 18 Mee ngulep Naan, ɗe a wur kǝ tap wus, wur jì put a npee wus mbezuum ɗi, wur pet ngulep Naan ɗe wur kǝ jeem ɗesese sǝ shi ɗoo ɗeɓal nǝnee, <<A mang jeem fwa, kǝ a yaa saa tuun laatǝng anab ɗi mǝ ɓǝm yil ɗesǝ nǝ, mbǝɗe laatǝng anab nǝ mo kǝ nung.>>
\v 19 Ngulep Naan nǝ wur wiit jeem wur nkaa yil nǝ, ɓe wur yaa saa tuun anab mo, ɗangɓe wur le mo nɗǝǝn pee ɗwat am anab, ɗe nǝ a tuup Naan ɗǝɗes.
\v 20 Mo tǝreng, kǝ mo ɗwat làa anab nǝ mo, aɓwoon yilkaam nǝ. Toom put nɗǝǝn làa anab ɗesǝ nǝ mo, mɓe toom nǝ sham kaa am sǝ, ɗe jong nǝ wul meel mo ngal mǝndong kǝ kambil peemee, kǝ jurum nǝ a kaa kám kǝ shii mo paat sǝ.
\c 15
\s1 Nenlep mo pwoovǝl // kǝ jeel mo pwoovǝl
\p 
\v 1 Ɗang wen naa, mee mbiinaaman ɗǝɗes, ɗe nǝ ɗee a mbii aapwoo nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan. Wen naa nenlep Naan mo pwoovǝl, kǝ jeel ɗe mǝ kyes nǝ mo pwoovǝl zak. A shi jeel ɗesǝ mo, ɓe Naan wur woo kyes kǝ tuup wur.
\v 2 Ɗangɓe wen naa, mee mbǝɗe nǝn nciit kǝ am baahar mǝ gǝlas, ɗe mo riyeep nǝ ashak kǝ wus, Nen ɗe mo se koorong nkaa luwa sǝ, kǝ nkaa muriin wur, kǝ nkaa gwar ɗe sǝm wur a sǝmɗuu (lambaa), moo ɗar ɗe mpwoo gǝnǝ nǝ. Mo kǝ ndeng-ndeng mo nsar mo, ɗe Naan wur shin mo,
\v 3 ɗangɓe mo cin kook mǝ Mosis kǝrem Naan, kǝ kook Laatǝm nǝ, mo cin kook nǝ nǝnee,
\q1 <<Ɗak fwa nǝ mo a ɗǝnan-nan mo,
\q1 ɗe mo aapwoo,
\q2 Daa Naan ɗe ɓal met jir.
\q1 Ar fwa nǝ mo a ɗe ndǝre, kǝ mo azeen-nzeen zak,
\q2 Mishkoom mǝ gurum ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil nǝ mo jir.
\q1 
\v 4 A wii nkǝǝr waa kas ye,
\q2 Daa? Kǝzak, a wii nnook kwoop sǝm fwa ye?
\q1 Daa a waa mmǝsak, a ɗeɓang.
\q1 Gurum ɗe nɗǝǝn yil mo jir, mo njì
\q2 seyil nwaa.
\q1 Mɓeeɗe gurum mo jir,
\q1 mo kǝ woo ɗak fwa
\q2 ɗe ndere nǝ mo.>>
\p 
\v 5 Aɓwoon ɗese, ɓe nghan naapee aɗengnaan, ɓe nghan naa mo wangpee ɗeɓang mǝ bit mǝ Naan, ɗe nǝ a langteng kǝ pwoo ɗe gyet Naan wur kǝ ten tuweer ne.
\v 6 Nenlep Naan mo pwoovǝl, ɗe mo kǝ jeel mǝ kyes ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ, mo jì put ndǝǝn Lu Naan ɗǝɗes, ɗe nǝ a mǝ Bìt Daa nǝ. Mo jwal a lée ɗeɓang, fuwaat ɗemǝlep mo, ɗe moo mangyit. Mo ɓwoot tuur fur mo shi zaal ɗe mo ɗak mo a shi zinariya.
\v 7 Memee ndǝǝn mbii ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ shin ɗaa shool mǝ zinariya mo pwoovǝl, nenlep Naan ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo. Ɗaa shool ɗesǝ nǝ mo gam kǝ tuup Naan ɗe wur kǝ seen ɗeɗǝm ngaa-ngaa.
\v 8 Ɓǝ Lu Naan ɗeɗes nǝ gam kǝ ɗyeel mǝ ɗeɗes wur, kǝ iiko wur zak. Baa mee gurum mak ɗel nɗǝǝn Lu Naan ɗeɗes nǝ kas, see aɓwoon ɗe jeel ɗe pwoovǝl mǝ nenlep ɗǝ pwoovǝl nǝ mo gam.
\c 16
\s1 Daa mo pwoovǝl mǝ tuup Naan
\p 
\v 1 Ɗangɓe nghan kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ɗeɓal nɗǝǝn Lu Naan ɗeɗes nǝ, nǝ sat nenlep kǝ Naan ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo nǝnee, <<Wu dǝm wu ɗoo mbii ɗe ndǝǝn ɗaa shool ɗe pwoovǝl ɗi mǝ tuup Naan nǝ mo nkaa yil ne.>>
\v 2 Ngulep Naan ɗinshee wur dǝm ɗoo mbii ɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa shool ɗe wur kǝ nǝ nkaa yil nǝ. Ɗangɓe sǝrep ɗeshwal ɗe mo bish naa, mo pwas nen ɗe mo kǝ fili (alaama) mǝ luwa nkaa sut sǝ, kǝ nen ɗe ɗi mo seyil mmuriin kǝ luwa ne.
\p 
\v 3 Ngulep Naan ɗevǝl wur dǝm ɗoo mbǝɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa ɗe wur kǝ nǝ nkaa baahar, ɗangɓe am nǝ cǝǝr ɗee kaa toom kǝ ngu mumuut sǝ. Mɓe ɗe mo kǝ seen ɗe moo tong nɗǝǝn am, mo murap jir.
\p 
\v 4 Ngulep Naan ɗekun, wur dǝm ɗoo mbǝɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa ɗe wur kǝ nǝ nkaa gǝnǝ am mo, kǝ tuɓut mo. Am nǝ mo cǝǝr ɗee a toom.
\v 5 Wen kǝlǝng ngulep ɗe wur tap kǝ am mo, wur sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Waa a ɗin ndǝret,
\q1 mbǝ canɗyeel ɗesǝ mo,
\q2 Waa a ɗeɓang,
\q1 waa ɗe gyet yam, ɓǝ waa ɗǝ,
\q2 waa ɗe waa ɗe yaksǝ.
\q1 
\v 6 Mɓeeɗe gyet mo ɓeer toom
\q1 kǝ nen fwa mo,
\q2 kǝ toom nensatpwoo fwa mo zak,
\q1 <<Mbe waa kǝ shin toom
\q2 mo shwaa ntiit-ntiit kǝ kwat mo.>>
\q1 
\v 7 Ɗangɓe nghan kǝlǝng mee ɗoo
\q2 a peewus mbezuum nǝ sat zak nǝnee,
\q1 <<Ii, Daa Naan ɗeɓal met jir.
\q1 Azeen-nzeen, canɗyeel fwa nǝ mo azeen,
\q2 kǝ mo a ndǝre zak.>>
\p 
\v 8 Ngulep Naan ɗefeer, wur dǝm ɗoo mbǝɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa ɗe wur kǝ nǝ, nkaa puus. Ɗangɓe mo cínɓal mpuus nǝ, mbǝkǝ nǝ caan gurum mo ɗe shi wus.
\v 9 Tal kǝ puus nǝ fes ɓaan gurum mo, shiɓal, mbe mo satpwoo ɗebuu nkaa sǝm kǝ Naan, ɗe wur kǝ iiko nkaa jeel nǝ mo. Mbe mo chi tuwap, baa mo kwoop ɗeɗes Naan kas.
\p 
\v 10 Ngulep Naan ɗepaat, wur dǝm ɗoo mbǝɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa ɗe wur kǝ nǝ, nkaa pee mǝ mulki mǝ luwa nǝ. Ɗangɓe mulki kǝ luwa nǝ cǝǝr ɗee a peenkoo. Ɓe gurum mo ǝrap liis fur mo mbǝ jeel ɗe mo nkaa shwaa ne.
\v 11 Gurum mo waa satpwoo ɗebuu nkaa Naan, mbǝ shwaajeel ɗe mo nkaa shwaa nǝ, kǝ sǝrap mo mo zak, mɓe jir kǝse, ɓe mo chi tuwap, mbǝ ɗak ɗebish ɗe mo kǝ ten cin mo.
\p 
\v 12 Ngulep Naan ɗepeemee, wur dǝm ɗoo mbǝɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa ɗe wur kǝni, nkaa gǝnǝ Yufrates ɗeɗes sǝ, ɓe am ɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn gǝnǝ ɗesǝ nǝ ɗel fii, mbǝkǝ nǝ ɗak ar ɗe mishkoom ɗe mo njì nkoop puus kǝkàa.
\v 13 Ɗangɓe nghan naa riin ɗebish mo kun, ɗe mo kaa nzargook mo sǝ, mo jì put nɗǝǝn pwoo kǝ kus nwòo sǝ, kǝ nɗǝǝn pwoo kǝ luwa sǝ, kǝ nɗǝǝn pwoo kǝ ngusatpwoo Naan mǝ ɗung sǝ.
\v 14 Riin ɗebish ɗesǝ nǝ mo nkaa cin mbǝ aapwoo mo ɗes hakyeng. Mo dǝm pee mishkoom mǝ yil ɗesǝ mo jir, mbǝkǝ mo kyak mo le ɗe ashak mbǝ cin lek parpuus ɗeɗes mǝ Naan ɗeɓal met jir sǝ.
\p 
\v 15 <<Wu naa nghan njì a kaa wat sǝ! Nen ɗe mo tong shi gongpee, ɗe mo kǝ lée fur mo a lǝlep, mbǝkǝ taji mo put ngum, kǝ mo kat naashwoop ɗe kas, ɓe nen mǝnǝ mo nkat ɗeret.>>
\p 
\v 16 Riin ɗebish ɗesǝ nǝ mo kyak mishkoom mǝ yil ɗesǝ mo le ashak, mmee mɓeɗǝ moo pet nǝ shi lespwoo mǝ nen Yahudi mo a Armageddon.
\v 17 Ngulep ɗepwoovǝl, wur dǝm ɗoo mbǝɗe nǝ nɗǝǝn ɗaa ɗe wur kǝnǝ nkaa kut. Ɗang mee ɗoo ɗeɓal jì put nɗǝǝn Lu kǝ Naan ɗǝɗes, a peetong mǝ mulki nǝ nǝnee, <<Nǝ kǝ shin!>>
\v 18 Kǝzak, pee nǝ mǝlep, nluupet, kǝ pee nǝ gwan. Yil nǝ yoon shiɓal, ɗe baa yil kǝ kyam yoon kaa mǝnǝ sǝ kas, pǝgyet ɗe gurum mo yaa tong ɗe ndǝǝn yil ne.
\v 19 Bǝrnǝn ɗeɗes nǝ ɓàk kun, kǝ kaar yil ɗe ndǝǝn yil nǝ mo jir, mo shirip. Naan wur pan Babilon ɗeɗes sǝ, mbe wur cin kap ɗe nǝ gam kǝ am anab (filip) ɗe nǝ a mǝ tuup wur nwura shwaa.
\v 20 Koo rep laayil ɗeɗangyi ɗe am neer nǝ cǝǝrkaat, ɓe nǝ su dǝm loom, kǝ ɗengjwak mo su dǝm laam zak.
\v 21 Ɗaar ɗǝnan-nan mo put nɗengnaan, mbe mo sham taa nkaa gurum mo, koo a ɗaar ɗeɗangyi ɓe toon kǝ nǝ wul kaa mǝ bufu kǝǝn sǝ. Gurum mo satpwoo ɗebuu nkaa Naan, mbǝ shwal ɗe moo shwaa nǝ, mbǝ sham kǝ ɗaar ɗesǝ nǝ mo, kǝ zak, mɓeeɗe jeel nǝ fes shwal zam hakyeng.
\c 17
\s1 Mat ngaa ɗeɗes kǝ luwayil sǝ
\p 
\v 1 Memee mɓut nenlep Naan ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo ɗe mo kǝ ɗaa mo pwoovǝl sǝ wur jì mpee nghan ɗǝ, ɓe wur sat nghan nǝnee, <<A jì, ɓe nghan nkám nwaa, kar ɗe mo can mmat ngaa ɗeɗes nǝ ɗǝ war kǝ tong pǝkom am mo.
\v 2 Mishkoom ɗe mǝ yil ɗesǝ mo cin ngaa ashak kǝ war, kǝ gurum ɗe nɗǝǝn yil ɗesǝ mo fes yuur kǝ am anab mǝ ngaa war nǝ.>>
\v 3 Ɓe la lep Naan mang an seet kǝ nǝ ɓut Riin, sǝ dǝm a naaryil, a npee ɗe baa am ɗe kas. A naaryil nǝ, ɓe nghan naa mee mat kǝ tong nkaa mee luwayil ɗe nǝ a naat. Mo ran sǝm ɗebish mo, ɗe mo satpwoo ɗebuu nkaa Naan. Luwayil ɗesǝ nǝ kǝ káa mo pwoovǝl, kǝ soom mo kaapaat.
\v 4 Mat nǝ war tap jwal a lée ɗe mo pan a naat mo ɗe mo ret naa zam, war kǝ tap ɗak mo a shi mbǝɗe mo ɗak mo a shi zinariya kǝ ngǝk ɗeapwus mo, kǝ mbii jwat ɗe rǝret mo, kaa mbǝɗe moo pet nǝ a peyal mo sǝ. Mat nǝ war kǝ mee ɗekwat nsar war, ɗe mo ɗak a shi zinariya, ɗe nǝ gam kǝ mbǝ ɗebish mo, ɗe mo a mǝ ar tong war ɗebish mǝ ngaa.
\v 5 Sǝm ɗǝ Mo ran nkaa pǝkeen war nǝ a bii ɗe mo manshi nǝ kas. BABILON ƊEƊES, NƏƏN MAT nGAA MO, KƏ mBƏ ƊEBISH ƊE MO nƊƏƏN YIL NƏ JIR.
\v 6 Wen naa mat nǝ war kǝ yuur shi toom nen Naan ɗe ɓang mo, Toom nen ɗe gyet mo shin langtǝng kǝ Jesu. Kaaɗe naa war, ɓe nǝ fes aapwoo nghan zam.
\v 7 Ngulep Naan wur tal pǝ nghan nǝnee, <<A mii aapwoo nwaa yii? Wen woo shii mbǝ ɗe baa a manshi nǝ kas kaa mat nǝ kǝ luwayil ɗe war kǝ lang kaa nǝ ɗe nǝ kǝ káa mo pwoovǝl, kǝ soom mo kaapaat sǝ.
\v 8 Luwayil ɗe a naa sǝ, ɗǝ gyet yam ɓe nǝ di, mɓe yaksǝ, baa nǝ kuɗi kas, nǝn yool kàa put a nɗǝǝn tuun ɗe baa nii peeɗar kas sǝ, mbǝkǝ nǝ dǝm ɗe a npeeɗe mo ntu nǝ ɗe vit. Nen ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil ɗese, ɗe pǝgyet ɗe nshee kǝ yil nǝ, ɓe baa mo ran sǝm mo mo nɗǝǝn buthaal mǝ seen kas. Nin aapwoo mo mbǝ naa luwayil ɗesǝ nǝ, mbǝɗe gyet nǝ ɗi kǝ seen, mɓe nǝ kǝ muut, jir kǝsǝ, ɓe nǝ nwaa baaji put kǝ seen zak.
\p 
\v 9 <<Ɗǝsǝ kǝ rǝɓet a pǝtuup ɗe kǝ seen manshi bii mo. Káa ɗe pwoovǝl nǝ mo, mo a zuul mo pwoovǝl, ɗe mat nǝ war tong nkaa mo sǝ.
\v 10 Mo a mishkom mo pwoovǝl zak. Mo kǝ sham kǝ paat mo ndǝǝn mulki mo, mɓe mǝndong ɗe nkaa se mulki yaksǝ. Baa ɗevǝl nǝ kǝ jì wul kas, mɓe katɗang wur njì wul, ɓe wur nse mulki nǝ a mbǝ rep pee lee ɓejee ɗak.
\v 11 Luwayil ɗe ɗi nǝ ɗi, yaksǝ baa nǝ kuɗi kas, a nǝ a mishkoom ɗepwookun nǝ. Mɓe nǝ a nɗǝǝn soon mishkoom ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo. Ɓe nǝ nkaa dǝm a pee ɗe mo tǝkook kǝ nǝ.
\p 
\v 12 <<Soom ɗekaapaat ɗe a naa sǝ mo, mo a mishkoom mo kaapaat, ɗe baa mo kǝcin mulki mo kas aku. Ɓe mbǝ awa mǝndong, ɓe mo ncin iiko mo kaa mishkoom mo sǝ, kǝ mo cin mulki ɗe ashak kǝ luwayil ne.
\v 13 Mishkoom ɗekaapaat sǝ mo, pan mo nǝ mo a ɗemǝndong, mo ncin ɓal mo, kǝ iiko mo nluwayil ne.
\v 14 Mo ncìn lek kǝ Laatǝm nǝ, mɓe Laatǝm nǝ wur nse koorong nkaa mo, mbǝɗe a wur a Daa ndaa mo, Mishkoom kǝ mishkoom mo, ashak kǝ wur, ɓe nen ɗe wur kǝ ten pǝrep, kǝ bǝlǝp mo, mo nse koorong zak.>>
\p 
\v 15 Ɗangɓǝ ngulepnaan wur sat nghan nǝnee, <<Am ɗe a naa sǝ, a mpeeɗǝ mat ngaa sǝ war tong ɗǝ, gurum mo, kuur gurum mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ yil mo shinǝ-shinǝ, kǝ liispwoo mo shinǝ-shinǝ zak.
\v 16 Soom ɗe kaapaat ɗe a naa sǝ mo, kǝ luwayil nǝ, mo mɓǝ cii mat ngaa nǝ. Mo mbǝ tǝkook kǝ mbii ɗǝ war kǝ nǝ mo jir, mbǝ mo yit war ɗee ngum, mo nse luwa war, kǝ mo ncaan war shi wus.
\v 17 A Naan wur kǝ ten le mǝnǝ nɗǝǝn pǝtuup mo, mbǝkǝ mo cin mbǝɗe nǝ gam ɗyen wur ɗǝ, kaaɗǝ mo ɓalkaa mo mo, mbǝkǝ mo shínɓal mo mo, mbǝ se mulki kǝ luwayil nǝ, mbe parɗi pwoonaan nǝ gam.
\v 18 Mat ɗe nwaa a naa nǝ, a yil ɗeɗes ɗe nǝ kǝ cin mulki, nkaa mishkoom mǝ yil nǝ mo.>>
\c 18
\s1 Pal Bǝrnǝn mBabilon
\p 
\v 1 Aɓwoon ɗese, ɓǝ nghan naa mee ngulepnaan npoo kǝ sham nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan. Ngulepnaan ɗesǝ wur kǝ iiko ɗeɗes zam. Mɓǝ peeɓang mǝ iiko wur nǝ ɓang yil nǝ kǝdǝng.
\v 2 Shi ɗoo ɗeɗes ɓe wur le or:
\q1 <<Ɓal fi kǝ kyes! Ɓal fi kǝ kyes!
\q2 Yil nBabilon ɗeɗes
\q1 War kǝ ɗee a tulu
\q2 riin ɗebish mo
\q1 War ɗee a peetong mǝ
\q2 koo a riin ɗebish ɗeɗangyii,
\q1 War ɗee a peetong mǝ
\q1 koo a mbǝ ɗerap,
\q2 kǝ nyer ɗebish.
\q1 Kǝ koo a luwa ɗeɗang ɗe nyakkap.
\q1 
\v 3 Mɓeeɗe gyet gurum nyil mo shini-shini, gyet mo shwaa a am anab
\q2 mǝ ngaa ashak kǝ war.
\q1 Mishkoom mǝ yil ɗǝsǝ mo
\q2 gyet mo cin ngaa kǝ war
\q1 Kǝ nennwer
\q1 ɗe mǝ yil ɗesǝ mo,
\q2 moo long a shi lǝɓet mbǝ bii
\q1 kǝ kat war ɗe mǝ yil ɗese, ɗe nǝ met mǝ sat.>>
\s1 Kar Bǝ Dyeel Ɗe // Nǝ Mbǝ Taa nBabilon
\q1 
\v 4 Ɗangɓe wen kǝlǝng mee ɗoo npoo
\q2 ɗe nǝ put nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan, nǝ sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Wun nen fǝn mo,
\q2 wu put aku ndǝǝn war,
\q1 mɓekǝ taji mo cin kwat nwun ashak kǝ war mbǝ shikbish war nǝ mo kas,
\q2 Mɓekǝ taji wu lap memee nɗǝǝn jeel war nǝ mo kas.
\q1 
\v 5 Mbǝɗǝ shikbish war nǝ mo kǝ ak
\q2 kàa wul a ɗengnaan,
\q1 Naan kǝ yee
\q2 ɗakɗebish war mo.
\q1 
\v 6 Wu kwat war nciit
\q2 kǝ mbii ɗǝ war kǝ cin wun,
\q1 wu kwat war yitvǝl,
\q2 mbǝ mbii ɗe gyet war kǝ cin mo nwun.
\q1 Wu ɗoo mo yitvǝl, kaaɗe gyet
\q1 war kǝ kam nwun ɗin
\q2 ɗekwat war sǝ.
\q1 
\v 7 Wu yit kǝ kwat ɗe nǝ a mǝ kar kǝ jeel
\q2 ɗe war lap nǝ, nǝ ɗee nciit-nciit kǝ ram kǝ long ɗe gyet war shin nkáa war,
\q1 mɓeeɗe war nkaa ɗyeep kaa nnee
\q2 <wen a mishkoom ɗe mat. baa wen a matkaa,
\q1 baa wen cam
\q2 wal maap kas.>
\q1 
\v 8 Mɓemǝnǝ ɓe, jeel war nǝ mo njì taa
\q1 nkaa war ndi mman, mɓeeɗi a parpuus mǝndong,
\q2 ɓe muut kǝ maap, kǝ neen, mo ntaa nkaa war.
\q1 Ɗangɓe wus ncaan war,
\q2 mbǝɗe Daa Naan
\q1 ɗe wur ntokɗyeel nwar,
\q2 wur kǝ iiko ɗes.
\p 
\v 9 <<Katɗang mishkoom mǝ ɓǝm-yil ɗesǝ mo, ɗe gyet mo cin ngaa ashak kǝ war, ɗe gyet mo se pak long war nǝ mo ashak kǝ war, ɓe mo nnaa ɗyeel ɗe nǝ caan war, ɓe mo nwal kǝ maap mbǝ war.
\v 10 Mbee jeel ɗeɗes ɗe war shwaa nǝ. Ɓe kǝǝrmuut nyaa mo, mbǝ mo nɗar a jong-jong kǝ moo wal ɗǝ, kǝ mo nsat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Jeel! Jeel mɓee wii yil
\q2 ɗeɗes Babilon!
\q1 Yil ɗe gyet wii kǝ iiko ɗes,
\q1 nɗǝǝn awa mǝndong,
\q2 ɓe kyes fii nǝ jì wul!>>
\m 
\v 11 <<Nennwer ɗe mo ɓǝm-yil nǝ mo, mo nwal kǝ maap nkaa war, mbǝɗe baa mee ngwe kuɗi, nseet lée mo mo kas.
\v 12 Lée nwar ɗe mo a zinariya mo, kǝ mǝ azurfa mo, kǝ mǝ nghǝk ɗeret ɗe moo mǝlep nyilaknyilak, kǝ nlǝr ɗe rǝret mo shini-shini, kǝ nlǝr ɗe pan a naat mo, kǝ shiyeep ɗeret mo, kǝ mbii ɗe mo ɗak mo a shi oos nǝ mo, kǝ shiyeep ɗekǝrǝm mo, kǝ mbǝɗe mo ɗak mo a shi shool ɗeret mo, kǝ nghǝk ɗeret ɗe mǝ ɗyiklu mo,
\v 13 kǝ bii ɗe kǝ toos shangshang, kaa sinamon, kǝ le shǝta, meer, kǝ frankisens, kǝ mwoor ɗe gurum kǝ caan, mbǝkǝ wur kǝlǝng toos ɗeshang nǝ ɗe sǝ, kǝ mǝ am anab, kǝ mǝ mwoor paat, kǝ mǝ áas ɗeret mo, mǝ alkama, kǝ mǝ randong mo, kǝ tǝm mo, kǝ mǝ bǝring mo, kǝ mǝ keke bǝring, kǝ gurum mo ɗi mo sǝrep mo kaa kǝrem mo sǝ>>
\q1 
\v 14 Nennwer nǝ mo nsat nwar nǝnee,
\q2 <<Jir mbii ɗi rǝret ɗe ɗi yii leyit nkaa mo,
\q1 moo ɗel dǝm jee.
\q1 Long fii mo jir,
\q2 kǝ rak fii nǝ mo jir,
\q1 mo nloom.
\q2 Baa wii kuɗi
\q1 yii kat
\q2 mo ɗi zak kas.>>
\p 
\v 15 Nennwer ɗe mo seet kǝ mbii ɗesǝ mo, ɗe mo kat long pǝ war di, mo nɗar jong-jong, kǝ kǝǝrmuut fes yaa mo, mbǝ shwaajeel ɗe war nkaa shwaa nǝ mo nwal kǝ maap.
\v 16 Har mo nfwo ruruu nǝnee,
\q1 <<Jeel fii, jeel fii, wii yil ɗǝɗes,
\q2 gyet yam, ɓe wii yii jwal a lee mulki ɗi rǝret mo
\q1 ɗetap piyaa mo, kǝ ɗetap naat juwal mo.
\q1 Ɗi mo mǝlep shi zinariya,
\q2 kǝ shi nghǝk ɗekǝrǝm
\q1 ɗi mo,
\q2 kǝ lilliu.
\q1 
\v 17 nƊǝǝn awa mǝndong ɓejee,
\q2 ɓǝ long fii ɗeɗes sǝ mo ɗee a ɗebuu!>
\p Jir nentung tii am mo, kǝ gurum ɗe moo ghǝr mo ntii nǝ mo, kǝ nen ɗe moo kat mbii teer mo mo a nɗǝǝn baahar mo, das ɗesǝ mo jir, mo nɗar jong-jong, kǝ war.
\v 18 Katɗang mo nnaa ɗyeel mǝ caan war nǝ kàa, ɓe mo nfwo or shiɓal nǝnee, <Baa mo cam kat mee yil ɗeɗes kaa yil sǝ kas.>
\v 19 Mo kok yil le nkaa káa mo mo, ashak kǝ wal, kǝ maap nǝnee,
\q1 <<Jeel fii! Jeel fii, wii yil ɗeɗes,
\q2 Gyet yam ɓe nen
\q1 ɗe mo kǝ tii mo nkaa baahar,
\q1 moo kat long a mbǝ long fii,
\q2 mɓe ndǝǝn awa mǝndong,
\q1 ɓe wii ɗee
\q2 a ɗelǝloom jee!>
\q1 
\v 20 Wii ɗengnaan, yi cin retnyit,
\q1 mbǝ mbii ɗe nǝ kat yil ɗesǝ war.
\q2 Wu cin retnyit, wun nen Naan mo,
\q1 kǝ wun jeplep mo, kǝ nensatpwoo Naan mo,
\q2 mɓeeɗe Naan wur canɗyeel nwar,
\q1 mɓee mbii ɗe gyet war
\q2 kǝcin mo nwun.>>
\s1 Kyes mBabilon
\p 
\v 21 Ɗangɓe mee ngulep Naan ɗeɓal, wur mang mee nghǝk ɗeɗes kaa fin ɗyees ɗak sǝ, wur vwet nǝ nɗǝǝn am baahar, kǝ wur sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Mo mɓwet Babilon yil ɗeɗes
\q2 sǝ a shiɓal aasǝ zak,
\q1 baa mo nkuɗi
\q2 kǝ naa war ɗe zak kas.
\q1 
\v 22 Baa mo mbaa kǝlǝng wal kǝ ndeng-ndeng, kǝ ɗoo nenkook mo,
\q1 kǝ wal mɓel, kǝ wal nfeer mo nɗǝǝn wii Babilon kas.
\q2 Baa mo nwaa kat mee ngucìn ɗak shi sar,
\q1 mǝ koo a kaan ɗak ɗeɗangyi nɗǝǝn wa kas.
\q2 Baa mo waa baa kǝlǝng
\q1 wal nfin ɗyees
\q2 ɗakmo nɗǝǝn wii kas.
\q1 
\v 23 Baa mee wus ngyem nwaa baa ɓangpee ɗi nɗǝǝn wii kas.
\q2 Baa mo waa baa kǝlǝng mee ɗoo mǝshpwoo kǝ matpoo nɗǝǝn wii kas.
\q1 Gyet yam, ɓe nennwer fii nǝ mo, a nen ɗǝnan-nan mǝ yil nǝ mo.
\q2 Gyet a shi mulgut mǝ soot fii,
\q1 ɓe yii le gurum ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil nǝ mo jir,
\q2 mo taa mer ar ɗi buu.
\q1 
\v 24 Gyet a nɗǝǝn Babilon,
\q1 ɓe mo kat toom
\q2 nensatpwoo Naan mo,
\q2 kǝ toom mǝ nen Naan mo, kǝ toom mǝ gurum
\q2 ɗe gyet mo saa mo jir nɗǝǝn ɓǝm-yil nǝ.>>
\c 19
\s1 kwoop Naan Ɓe Pal mBabilon
\p 
\v 1 Aɓwoon ɗese, ɓe nghan kǝlǝng mee ɗoo ɗe nǝ kaa ɗoo ɗeɗes, mǝ gurum mo ɗeɗes sǝ nɗǝǝn ɗengnaan. Ɗoo nǝ mo sat nǝnee,
\q1 << kwoop Naan!
\q1 Mɓeeɗe ɓam, kǝ ram,
\q2 kǝ iiko mo a mǝ Daa Naan fun.
\q1 
\v 2 Mɓeeɗe canɗyeel wur
\q2 nǝ azeen, kǝ nǝ a ndǝret.
\q1 Wur kǝ canɗyeel ɗebish, mmat ngaa sǝ.
\q1 Ɗe gyet war tǝkook yil nǝ shi ngaa war sǝ.
\q2 Wur baa kwat war,
\q1 nciit kǝ toom kǝ kǝrem
\q2 wur ɗe gyet war twe mo.>>
\p 
\v 3 Kǝzak, mo waa baa fwo or shiɓal nǝnee,
\q1 << kwoop Naan!
\q1 Ɗyeel ɗe mo caan war
\q2 nǝ nkàa ɗeng ngaa-ngaa.>>
\p 
\v 4 Nennan ɗe laarvǝl baafeer sǝ mo, kǝ mbii ɗefeer ɗe mo kǝ seen sǝ mo, mo kurum nyil, kǝ mo seyil ɗe nNaan, ɗe wur tong a peetong mǝ mulki. Mo seyil nwur, mo sat nǝnee, <<Nǝ aa sǝ! Kwoop Naan!>>
\p 
\v 5 Ɗangɓe mee ɗoo jì put ɗe nɗǝǝn peetong mǝ mulki nǝ nǝnee,
\q1 <<Kwoop Naan fun,
\q2 wun kǝrem wur mo,
\q1 wun ɗe wuu kǝr wur,
\q2 nen ɗeɗyeen mo, kǝ nen ɗenan mo jir.>>
\m 
\v 6 Ɗangɓe wen kǝleng mee mbii kaa ɗoo kǝ gurum mo ɗes sǝ, nǝn nciit kǝ wal kǝ am ɗǝɗes, ɗe nii sham ndang, kǝ nǝ wal kaa nluu ɗe nii pet sǝ. Ɗoo nǝ mo sat nǝnee,
\q1 <<Kwoop Naan!
\q1 Mɓeeɗe Daa Naan fun ɗeɓal jir,
\q2 wur se mulki.
\q1 
\v 7 Wu yit kǝ mǝ cin retnyit shi pǝtuup ɗeɓang,
\q2 wu yit kǝ mǝ shin ɗeɗes nwur.
\q1 Mɓeeɗe pee nǝ wul, ɗe Laatǝm kǝ Naan wur ncìnɗyik.
\q2 Matpoo nǝ war kǝ ɗak seet mbǝ ɗyik nǝ.
\q1 
\v 8 Mo shin lée ɗepiyaa peng-peng mo nwar,
\q2 mɓekǝ war lep ɗi.>>
\q1 (Lée ɗepiyaa peng-peng nǝ mo,
\q2 moo kám a ɗak ɗeret ɗe nen Naan ɗe pang mo kǝ ten cin.)
\p 
\v 9 Ɗangɓe ngulep Naan wur sat nghan nǝnee, <<A ran ɗesǝ. Ɗeret nkaa nen ɗe mo pǝrep mo mbǝ se serǝɓet mǝ Laatǝm nǝ.>>
\m Ngulep Naan wur waa baa sat nghan nǝnee, <<Ɗese nǝ a pwoo Naan azeen-nzeen.>>
\m 
\v 10 Wen saam nyil ntoom wur, mbǝkǝ nghan seyil ɗi nwur, mbǝ wur sat nghan nǝnee, <<Taji a cin mǝnǝ kas, nghan a kǝrem Naan kaa waa sǝ, <<kǝ koor ɗyemnǝǝn fun ɗe mo lap langteng mǝ Jesu sǝ. A seyil a nNaan.
\m Pwoo ɗe Jesu wur woo nǝ, a nǝ a káa riin nensatpwoo Naan mo.>>
\s1 Jeplek Ɗe a Ɗengnaan // Mo Se Koorong nKaa // Luwa Yil Nǝ
\p 
\v 11 Wen naa Ɗengnaan a wuwang, ɓe mee bǝring ɗepiyaa ɗe nii ɗar a kyen fen, ɗe sǝm kǝ gwar ɗe wur lang bǝring ɗepiyaa nǝ a Ngwe ɗe ndǝre, kǝ Nguzeen. Wur canɗyeel a ndǝǝn ar ɗe ndǝre, kǝ cin lek zak.
\v 12 Yit wur mo a kaa aawus sǝ, kǝ wur kǝ mbiikáa mǝ mulki mo ɗes nkaa káa wur zak. Wur kǝ mee sǝm ɗe nǝ a rǝran nkaa shin, ɗe baa mee gurum mak man nǝ kas, see a wur shikáa wur ɓejee ɗak.
\v 13 Wur lep lée ɗe sǝɓen ɗe mo kǝ lep ndǝǝn toom, kǝ sǝm wur nǝ a Pwoo Naan.
\v 14 Nenlek ɗe mo ndǝǝn ɗengnaan, moo mwaan nɗang wur nkaa bǝring ɗepiyaa-piyaa mo, kǝ mo tap lep a lee lilin ɗepiyaa kǝ ɗeɓang.
\v 15 Mee kwai ɗesese jì put mpwoo wur. A shi kwai ɗesǝ ɓe wur nsaa gurum ɗe mo nyil nǝ mo shinǝ-shinǝ, <<Wur nse mulki nkaa mo a shi ɗul shool.>> Wur ntǝreng am anab nǝ a peetǝreng anab ɗe nǝ a mǝ tuup Naan ɗeɓal met jir.
\v 16 Nkaa nlǝr wur, kǝ nkaa cìi wur, ɓe sǝm ɗe nǝ sat nǝnee, <<MISHKOOM MƏ MISHKOOM MO, DAA MƏ DAA MO.>>
\v 17 Ɓe nghan naa mee ngulep Naan wur ɗar nkaa puus, wur pǝrep nyer ɗe moo yool ncáap shi ɗoo ɗeɗes, nǝnee, <<Wu jì, wu kaat ashak jir, mbǝ gomteer ɗeɗes mǝ Naan.
\v 18 Mɓekǝ wuu se luwa mishkoom mo ɗi, kǝ luwa ɗenan-nan mǝ nenlek mo, kǝ luwa nen ɗǝnan-nan mo, kǝ luwa mǝ bǝring mo, kǝ mǝ nenlang bǝring nǝ mo, kǝ luwa gurum mo jir, mǝ jeplu mo, kǝ mǝ kǝrem mo, ɗeɗyeen, kǝ ɗenan.>>
\p 
\v 19 Wen naa luwayil sǝ, kǝ mishkoom mǝ yil nǝ mo, kǝ nenlek mo mo, mo kuur ashak, mbǝkǝ mo cin lek ɗi kǝ ngulang bǝring ɗepiyaa sǝ, kǝ nenlek wur mo.
\v 20 Mbǝ mo yaa luwayil nǝ ashak kǝ ngusatpwoo Naan mǝ ɗung sǝ, ɗe gyet wur cin mbii aapwoo, kǝ mbiinaaman mo a pee mǝ luwayil nǝ. A shi mbii aapwoo ɗesǝ mo, ɓe gyet wur num nen ɗe mo lap mbiinaaman mǝ luwayil nǝ, kǝ gyet mo seyil muriin wur zak. Mo vwet mo weet mmeen nɗǝǝn aawus ɗe nii lap a shi fwat mǝ bintǝka.
\v 21 Mo twe koor nǝ mo shi kwai ɗe nǝ jì put pwoo kǝ ngulang bǝring ɗepiyaa sǝ. Nyer mo jir, mo se luwa nǝ, mbǝ nǝ mak mo.
\c 20
\s1 Ɓit nGal Mǝndong
\p 
\v 1 Ɗangɓe Wen naa mee ngulep Naan kǝ sham put ndǝǝn ɗengnaan, wur kǝ biwangpee mǝ wang tuun ɗejurum, ɗe baa nii peeɗar kas sǝ, kǝ wur kǝ mee tǝzek ɗeɗes nsar wur.
\v 2 Wur yaa nwòo sǝ, nwòo ɗe pǝgyet nǝ ɗi yam-yam sǝ. A nwòo nǝ wur a ngujwan, ko shetan, Ngulep Naan wur ɓwoot ngujwaan mbǝ ɓit ngal mǝndong.
\v 3 Ngulep Naan nǝ vwet nwòo nǝ sham nɗǝǝn tuun ɗe baa nii peeɗar kas sǝ. Aɓwoon mǝnǝ, ɓe wur shoot pwoo tuun nǝ, kǝ wur lus nǝ, mbǝkǝ taji ngujwaan wur katpee mbǝ gwam gurum ɗe nɗǝǝn yil nǝ mo ɗi zak kas, see aɓwoon ɓit ngal mǝndong akuɗang. Aɓwoon mǝnǝ, ɓe mo mɓwet ngujwaan nǝ, mbǝ reppee lee ɗak.
\p 
\v 4 Ɗangɓe wen naa mbii tong mǝ mulki mo, kǝ zak, nen ɗe mo kǝ tong nkaa mbiitong mulki mo, moo shin ɓal mo bǝ tok ɗyeel. Wen naa seen nen ɗe gyet mo saa káa mo, mbǝɗe gyet mo shin camkat mbǝ Jesu, kǝ mbǝ pwoo Naan. Baa gyet moo seyil luwayil nǝ koo mǝ riin wur kas, kǝ baa gyet mo lap mbiinaaman mǝ luwayil nǝ nkaa pǝkyeen mo mo, koo nkaa sar mo mo kas. Mo baa shin seen mo, mbe mo se mulki ashak kǝ Kristi mbǝ ɓit duɓu mǝndong.
\v 5 Koor nen ɗǝ mumurap nǝ mo nkat seen kas, see mɓwoon ɓit mo ngal mǝndong akuɗang. A ɗesǝ nǝ a yool a pee muut ɗe nshee.
\v 6 Ɗǝret kǝ ɗǝɓang a nen ɗe mo mak yool a peemúut ɗinshee ɗiisi nǝ. Baa muut ɗevǝl mak katɓal nkaa mo kas, mɓǝ mo nɗe a pris mǝ Naan mo, kǝ mǝ Kristi, mbǝ mo nse mulki ashak kǝ wur mbǝ ɓit mo ngal mǝndong.
\s1 Can Ɗyeel nShetan
\p 
\v 7 Aɓwoon ɗe ɓit ngal mǝndong nǝ mo ɗel, ɓe mo nfwen shetan nɗǝǝn lushoot ɗe mo ɓwoot wur ɗǝ.
\v 8 Ɓe ngujwaan wur nput dǝm mbǝkǝ wur gwam gurum ɗe mo ndǝǝn yil nǝ mo ɗǝ, nɗǝǝn kwang ɗefeer mǝ yil nǝ. Yil ɗiisi nǝ mo a Gok, kǝ Magok, wur cak mo le ashak mbǝ lek. Ɗuu mo nǝ ɗee a kaa ɗyees mpwoo am baahar sǝ.
\v 9 Mo mpǝǝr nkaa yil nǝ jir, mbǝ mo ndǝm neer mpeeɗǝ nen Naan moo kuur ɗǝ, kǝ yil ɗe wur wal nnǝ. Ɗangɓǝ wus ntong a ɗengnaan sham se mo.
\v 10 Ɗangɓǝ ngujwaan ɗe gyet wur gwam mo, mo nvwet wur nɗǝǝn aawus ɗe nii lap a shi fwat mǝ bindǝga, nɓeeɗe luwayil nǝ kǝ ngusatpwoo Naan mǝ ɗung sǝ mo. Mo nshwaajeel a peemǝnǝ mpar kǝ puus, mbǝ ngaa-ngaa.
\s1 Tokɗyeel nen ɗe mo kǝ murep
\p 
\v 11 Ɗangɓǝ wen naa mee peetong mǝ mulki ɗeɗes a piyaa, gwar ɗe wur tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki ɗiisi nǝ, ɓe yil kǝ ɗengnaan mo loom ciir nyit wur, baa mee peeɗi bǝ kas.
\v 12 Wen naa nen mumuut, ɗenan, kǝ ɗeɗyeen mo kǝ ɗar toom mulki wur, ɓǝ bǝǝt-haal mo wang. Ɓǝ ɓǝǝt-haal pwoo wang ɗe nǝ a Ɓǝǝt-haal mǝ seen. Mo ntokɗyeel nen mumuut nǝ mo nkaa mbii ɗi moo cin kaaɗe mo kǝ ran ɗin ɓǝǝt haal nǝ mo sǝ. Mo ran mo nkaa ɗak ɗe gyet nen mumuut nǝ mo kǝ cin ɓe mo kutɗi mmeen.
\v 13 Bahar war shwat nen mumuut ɗe mo nɗǝǝn war, kǝ muut mǝ peemúut mo shwat nen mumuut ɗe mo nɗǝǝn mo, koo a ngwe ɗeɗang ye, mo tokɗyeel mo nciit-nciit kǝ mbii ɗe moo kǝ ten cin.
\v 14 Mɓǝ mo vwet muut kǝ peemúut nɗǝǝn aawus. Aawus ɗesǝ nǝ a peemúut ɗevǝl mmǝnǝ.
\v 15 Jir ngweɗe baa sǝm wur nǝ a rǝran nɗǝǝn bǝǝthaal mǝ seen kas, ɓe mo kǝ vwet gwar mǝnǝ nɗǝǝn aawus ne.
\c 21
\s1 Ɗengnaan ɗepwoo kǝ // yil ɗepwoo
\p 
\v 1 Wen naa ɗengnaan ɗepwoo kǝ ɓǝm-yil ɗepwoo, mbǝɗe ɗengnaan ɗinshee, kǝ ɓǝm-yil ɗinshee nǝ, mo kuɗi kas, kǝ baa mee baahar kuɗi kas.
\v 2 Wen naa yil ɗeɓang, Jerusalem ɗepwoo, nǝ sham put ndǝǝn ɗengnaan pee Naan ɗǝ. Mo tap ɗak war a kaa matpoo ɗe war lep lée rǝret mbǝ kaat kǝ mish war sǝ.
\v 3 Ɗangɓǝ nghan kǝlǝng mee ɗoo put a peetong mǝ mulki nǝ, nǝ sat nǝnee, <<Wu naa! Peetong Naan nǝ ashak kǝ gurum mo, wur ntong ashak kǝ mo. Mo mbǝ ɗee a nen wur mo, kǝ Naan wur shikáa fǝn ntong ashak kǝ mo, nwur nɗee a Naan mo zak.
\v 4 Wur mbǝ mpwes koo a yitmwaan ɗeɗangyi nɗǝǝn yit mo mo. Baa mee muut koo maap, koo wal, koo shwal kuɗi kas, mbǝɗe mbǝ deyam mo kǝ ɗel seet.>>
\p 
\v 5 Wur ɗe dǝ wur kǝ tong nkaa peetong mǝ mulki nǝ wur sat nǝnee, <<Wen nkaa ɗak koo meye, a ɗepwoo.>> Ɗangɓe wur sat nǝnee, <<A ran mbii ɗesǝ, mbǝɗe mo mak kǝ gurum shinzeen, kǝ mo azeen zak.>>
\p 
\v 6 Wur sat nghan nǝnee, <<Nǝ kǝ chin. A an a Alfa nǝ kǝ Omega, ɗinshee nǝ, kǝ kyes nǝ. Ngwe ɗe am tu wur, an bǝ shin am nwur nzuum, nɗǝǝn tuɓut mǝ am seen sǝ.
\v 7 Nen ɗǝ mo se koorong, ɓǝ mo nse kop mbii ɗesǝ mo jir. An nɗee a Naan mo, kǝ mo ɗee a jepfen mo.
\v 8 Mbǝ nenkǝrmuut mo, kǝ nencii cinzeen mo, kǝ nenɗebish mo, kǝ nentukáa mo, kǝ nenngaa mo, kǝ soot mo, kǝ nenseyil nkùm mo, kǝ nencìn ɗung mo, mo nfwo mo nɗǝǝn aawus ɗe nii lap wus a shi fwat mǝ bintǝka. Ɗese nǝ a muut ɗevǝl mmǝne.>>
\s1 Jerusalem ɗepwoo ne, // Matpoo nLaatǝm nǝ
\p 
\v 9 Memee mɓut nenlepnaan ɗe pwoovǝl sǝ mo, ɗe mo kǝ ɗaa mo pwoovǝl, gam kǝ jeel ɗe pwoovǝl mǝ kyes nǝ sǝ mo, jì sat nghan nǝnee, <<A jì, kǝ nghan kám matpoo nǝ ɗi ngha, ɗǝ war a mat nlaatǝm nǝ.>>
\v 10 Ɓǝ wur mang an seet kǝ nǝ ɗǝǝn Riin shin kaa aɗǝng zuul ɗǝdes ɗang wurang, kǝ wur kam pee yil ɗǝɓang nghan. Jerusalem nǝ tong aɗeng sham put pǝ Naan ɗi.
\v 11 Nǝ ɓangpee shi ram nNaan, kǝ ɓangpee nǝ a kaa mǝ jwak ɗekǝrǝm mo sǝ, kaa ɓangpee mǝ jaspa sǝ. Nǝ ɓangpee kyel-kyel!
\v 12 Nǝ kǝ mee kok ɗǝɗes, ɗewurang, ɗe nǝ kǝ polu mo kaapaat baavǝl. Nenlepnaan mo kaapaat baavǝl, moo ɗar mpolu ɗesǝ mo, Mo ran sǝm soon ɗekaapaat baavǝl mǝ nen Izrel mo nkaa polu ɗekaapaat baavǝl ɗesǝ nǝ mo.
\v 13 Dǝ polu mo kun nsar puus kaa, polu mo kun nkwang ndeel, polu mo kun nkwang ngyeen, kǝ mo kun nǝ sarpuus sham.
\v 14 Kok mǝ yil nǝ kǝ kuk mo kaapaat baavǝl. Mo ran sǝm jeplep ɗǝ kaapaat baavǝl Laatǝm nǝ mo nkaa mo.
\p 
\v 15 Ngulepnaan ɗe wur leshap kǝ nghan, wur kǝ mbiikám pee, ɗe mo ɗak nǝ a shi zinariya, mbǝkǝ wur kám yil nǝ ɗǝ, kǝ polu nǝ mo, kǝ kok nǝ mo.
\v 16 Shwàl nyil nǝ kǝ kaam nǝ, mo a nciit-nciit. Ngulepnaan nǝ wur kam yil nǝ, bǝ wur kat nǝ wul meel ngal kaapaat nɗǝǝn sǝɓen nyil nǝ, kǝ kaam nǝ, kǝ wurang nǝ nciit-nciit.
\v 17 Ngulepnaan nǝ wur waa kám kaam kok nǝ, ɓe nǝ a shii kambil mǝndong kǝ laarfeer baafeer ntoon kǝ nǝǝr nǝ.
\v 18 Mo ɗak kok nyil nǝ a shi jaspa, kǝ yil nǝ a shi zinariya kǝding-ding, nǝ mǝlep kaa mbiinaarin.
\v 19 Mo ɗak jwat nkuk kok mǝ yil nǝ mo shi nghǝk ɗǝret.
\q2 Moɗak kuk ɗinshee nǝ a shi jaspa,
\q2 ɗevǝl nǝ a shi safiya,
\q2 ɗekun nǝ a shi aget,
\q2 ɗefeer nǝ a shi emiral,
\q2 
\v 20 Ɗepaat nǝ a shi Onis,
\q2 ɗepeemee nǝ a shi rubi,
\q2 Ɗepwoovǝl nǝ a shi krisolait,
\q2 ɗepwookun nǝ a shi beril,
\q2 Ɗepwoofeer nǝ a shi topas,
\q2 ɗekaapaat nǝ a shi tokwes,
\q2 ɗekaapaat baamǝndong nǝ a shi jasinf,
\q2 ɗekaapaat baavǝl nǝ a shi ametis.
\v 21 Mo ɗak koo a pwoolu ɗeɗangyi ɗekaapaat baavǝl sǝ mo shi mee nghǝkɗeret ɗe moo pet nǝ a peyal. Koo a pwoolu ɗeɗang ye, ɓe nǝ mang peyal mǝndong. Ar ɗǝɗes ɗǝ nǝ nyilkaam nǝ mo mo ɗak a shi zinariya kǝdǝng-dǝng kaa binaariin sǝ.
\p 
\v 22 Baa wen naa mee Lu Naan ɗeɗes ɗe nɗǝǝn yil nǝ kas, mbǝɗe Daa Naan ɗeɓal met jir, kǝ Laatǝm nǝ, a mo a Lu Naan ɗǝɗes.
\v 23 Baa yil nii rǝɓet puus, koo tar mbǝ kǝnǝ ɓang nǝ ɗi kas, mbǝɗe ɗeɗes Naan nii ɓang yil nǝ jir, kǝ Laatǝm wur a ngyam yil ne.
\v 24 Ɓǝ song yil nǝ mo mwaan a nɗǝǝn peeɓang nǝ, kǝ mishkoom mǝ Ɓǝm-yil nǝ mo, mo njì kǝ ɗeɗes mo mo ndǝǝn nǝ.
\v 25 Baa mo cam shoot polu nǝ mo koo yit mǝndong kas, mbǝɗe baa mee paar nɗen ɗi kas.
\v 26 Ɓǝ yil nǝ mo bǝ ji kǝ ram, kǝ Long mo mo, nɗǝǝn nǝ jir.
\v 27 Baa mee mbii ɗerap mmak ɗel ɗe nɗǝǝn yil nǝ kas. Koo ngwe ɗe wur cin mbǝɗe mǝ nashweep, koo gwampee, ɓe baa mo cam ɗel nɗǝǝn yil nǝ kas, mɓe see a nen ɗe sǝm mo mo a rǝran ndǝǝn bǝǝthaal mǝ seen Laatǝm ɓejee ɗak.
\c 22
\s1 Geen ɗe Nǝ a Mǝ Seen
\p 
\v 1 Ɗangɓe ngulep Naan wur kám mee geen nghan, ɗe nǝ a mǝ am mǝ seen. Am nǝ ɗong yet-yet. Am nǝ put a peetong mǝ mulki Naan, kǝ mǝ Laatǝm ne.
\v 2 Am ɗesǝ nǝ sham a nnaar ar ɗeɗes mǝ yil nǝ. Tǝng mǝ seen nii ɗar mpwoo geen nǝ koo nkwang ɗeɗang ye. Nii làa-làa mo kaapaat baavǝl, koo tar ɗeɗangyi mǝ laatǝng mo. Kom tǝng ɗǝsǝ nǝ a mbǝ baar gurum ɗi mǝ yil nǝ mo jir, shinǝ-shinǝ.
\v 3 Baa mee mbii ɗebish mmak ɗel nɗǝǝn yil nǝ zak kas. Peetong mǝ mulki Naan kǝ Laatǝm, mo ntong nɗǝǝn yil nǝ, kǝ kǝrem wur mo nseyil nwur.
\v 4 Mo nnaa yit Naan, moo nnaa sǝm wur nkaa pǝkyeen mo mo.
\v 5 Baa mee par kuɗi zak kas. Baa mo nwaa kuɗi kǝ cin ɗak kǝ peeɓang mǝ ngyam zak kas, koo mǝ puus kas, mbǝɗe Daa Naan wur nshin peeɓang mo, kǝ mo nse mulki mbe ngaa-ngaa.
\s1 Ji nJesu
\p 
\v 6 Ngulepnaan wur sat nghan nǝnee, <<Pwoo ɗesǝ nǝ mo mak ɗe gurum nshínzeen mo, Kǝ mo azeen zak. Daa Naan ɗe wur cin Riin wur nensatpwoo wur mo, wur lep ngulep wur, mbǝkǝ ngulep nǝ wur kám ɗin nkǝrem wur mo, mbii ɗe a ting mo ncìn akyeen kǝlak.>>
\p 
\v 7 <<Jesu sat nǝ nee, Wu naa, nghan kǝ jì kǝlak-kǝlak! Ɗeret nkat ngwe ɗe wur tap pwoo ɗǝ nen satpwoo nan mo ran nɗǝǝn ngarvit ɗesǝ.>>
\p 
\v 8 A nghan Joon, a an a ngweɗe nkǝlǝng, ɗang nnaa mbii ɗesǝ mo, kaaɗe nghan kǝlǝng ɗang nghan naa mo, ɓǝ nghan taa nyil shii ngulepnaan nǝ kǝ nghan seyil ɗe wur dǝ kǝ kám mbii ɗesǝ nǝ mo nghan.
\v 9 Mbe wur sat nghan nǝnee, <Taji a seyil nghan kas, nnǝ wuɗin a kǝrem kaa nghan sǝ, kǝ ɗyemnǝǝn fun nensatpwoo Naan mo, kǝ jir nen ɗe moo tap kǝ pwoo ɗerǝran nɗǝǝn bǝǝthaal ɗesǝ nǝ. Wu seyil a nNaan!>
\p 
\v 10 Ngulep nǝ wur sat nghan nǝnee, << Pwoo Naan ɗe mo nɗǝǝn bǝǝthaal ɗesǝ, taji a paa mo kas, mbǝɗe pee nǝ wul, mbǝkǝ mbii ɗesǝ nǝ mo cin ɗi.
\v 11 Wu yit kǝ ngucìn mbii ɗebish mo, ɓe wur sekyeen kǝ cin nǝ. Wu yit kǝ ngucìn mbii ɗerap mo, ɓe wur sekyeen kǝ chin mo. Ngucìn mbii ɗin ndǝre mo, wu yit kǝ wur sekyeen kǝ cin ɗin ndǝre wur. Ngwe ɗe wur a ɗeɓang ɓe wur sekyeen ɗe a ɗeɓang.>>
\v 12 <<Wu naa, nghan pǝ jì kǝlak-kǝlak ashak kǝ kwat fǝn. Wen shin nǝ nkòo a weye, nciit-nciit kǝ mbii ɗe gurum kǝ ten cin mo.
\v 13 Wen a Alfa kǝ Omega, ɗe a nghan a Tǝleng kǝ mbii mo, kǝ ɗe mɓwoon kǝ mo, nghan a Ɗinshee kǝ Kyes kǝ mbii mo jir zak.
\p 
\v 14 Nen ɗe mo vwang lée mo mo ɓang-ɓang, ɓe mo nkat ɗeret, mbǝɗe a mo nkat iiko mbǝ se laatǝng ɗǝ mǝ seen nǝ, kǝ mo nɗel mpolu nǝ mo, mbǝ ɗel nɗǝǝn yil ne.
\v 15 Mɓwoon yil nǝ, ɓe as mo ɗi, kǝ soot mo, kǝ nenngaa mo, kǝ nentukáa mo, kǝ nenseyil nkùm mo, kǝ jir nen ɗe mo rǝɓet cìn ɗung mo.
\p 
\v 16 A nghan a Jesu kǝn lep ngulep fen, mbǝkǝ wur shin langteng ɗesǝ mo nwaa, mbǝ Ekǝlisya mo. A nghan a cirem kǝ dang Devit, kǝ a nghan a Tar mangɓit, ɗe nii ɓangpee sǝ.>>
\p 
\v 17 Riin nǝ kǝ matpoo nǝ, mo sat nǝnee, <<A jì!>> Wu yit kǝ koo a weye, ɗe wur kǝlǝngpee, ɓe wur sat nǝnee, <<A jì.>> Wu yit kǝ koo a weye ɗe neen am tu wur, mbǝ am mǝ seen, ɓe wu yit kǝ wur jì, mbǝkǝ wur lap am mǝ seen nǝ shwaa ɗe shi zuum.
\p 
\v 18 Wen Joon pǝ dul kom kòo a weye shiɓal nee koo a weyii ɗe wur kǝlǝng pwoo ɗe mo ran ndǝǝn ngarvit ɗesǝ, ɗe mo put pee Riin Naan ɗi. Katɗang mee gurum le mee pwoo nkaa ɗe mo kǝ ten ran nɗǝǝn ngarvit ɗesǝ nǝ, ɓe Naan wur le kwat pwoo ngwar mǝnǝ a shi jeel ɗe mo kǝ ten ran nɗǝǝn ngarvit ɗesǝ.
\v 19 Katɗang mee ngwe mang mee mbii baa kǝ nǝ ndǝǝn pwoo ɗe mo a rǝran, ɗe mo put a pee Riin Naan nɗǝǝn ngarvit ɗesǝ, ɓe Naan mbǝ mang pak pwoo mǝwur ndǝǝn tǝng mǝ seen kǝ ndǝǝn Yil Ɗebang, kaaɗǝ mo kǝ sat nɗǝǝn ngarvit ɗesǝ.
\p 
\v 20 Gwar ɗe wu shin camkat mbǝ mbii ɗesǝ nǝ mo jir, wur sat nǝnee, <<Ii, nghan pǝ ji kǝlak-kǝlak. Nǝ akǝsǝ. A jì, Daa Jesu.>>
\v 21 Ɗeret Daa Jesu tong ashak kǝ wun jir. Naasǝ.
